data-message-id="c28e91c2-0bde-4575-b795-c6283592cde8" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-thinking"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="140">可以的，完全能用 Python + Selenium 实现你要的流程。我已经帮你把一个<strong data-start="43" data-end="55">可直接运行的脚本</strong>放到你的工作区里了（含 PDF→逐页 PNG、上传截图、在 ProseMirror 输入框里提问、等待回答、把“图片+回答”一页页追加到一个 Markdown 文件里）：</p>
<p data-start="142" data-end="207"><span class="" data-state="closed"><a data-start="142" data-end="207" class="cursor-pointer">下载脚本：auto_qa_from_pdf.py</a></span></p>

<li data-start="359" data-end="444">
<p data-start="362" data-end="444"><strong data-start="362" data-end="381">把你的 PDF 放到脚本同目录</strong>，命名成 <code data-start="386" data-end="397">input.pdf</code><br data-start="397" data-end="400">
（或打开脚本顶部 <code data-start="409" data-end="417">CONFIG</code>，把 <code data-start="420" data-end="431">input_pdf</code> 改成你的文件名/路径。）</p>
</li>

<ol start="5" data-start="823" data-end="834">
<li data-start="823" data-end="834">
<p data-start="826" data-end="834"><strong data-start="826" data-end="834">产出在哪</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<ul data-start="835" data-end="1022">
<li data-start="835" data-end="1022">
<p data-start="837" data-end="856">所有生成文件在 <code data-start="845" data-end="856">./output/</code></p>
<ul data-start="859" data-end="1022">
<li data-start="859" data-end="920">
<p data-start="861" data-end="920"><code data-start="861" data-end="880">./output/notes.md</code>：你的备课 Markdown（每页一段：图片 + “什么意思？详细解释”的回答）</p>
</li>
<li data-start="923" data-end="962">
<p data-start="925" data-end="962"><code data-start="925" data-end="942">./output/pages/</code>：直接从 PDF 渲染出来的逐页 PNG</p>
</li>
<li data-start="965" data-end="1022">
<p data-start="967" data-end="1022"><code data-start="967" data-end="991">./output/notes_assets/</code>：写入到 Markdown 的图片副本（MD 相对引用更稳定）</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1024" data-end="1027">
<h2 data-start="1029" data-end="1042">脚本做了什么（概览）</h2>
<ul data-start="1044" data-end="1460">
<li data-start="1044" data-end="1119">
<p data-start="1046" data-end="1119">用 <strong data-start="1048" data-end="1066">PyMuPDF (fitz)</strong> 把 PDF 每页渲染为 PNG（默认 180 DPI，你可以在 <code data-start="1099" data-end="1111">render_dpi</code> 调高/调低）。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1120" data-end="1161">
<p data-start="1122" data-end="1161">启动 <strong data-start="1125" data-end="1135">Chrome</strong>（可切换 <code data-start="1140" data-end="1155">headless=True</code> 静默跑）。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1162" data-end="1460">
<p data-start="1164" data-end="1169">对每一页：</p>
<ol data-start="1172" data-end="1460">
<li data-start="1172" data-end="1237">
<p data-start="1175" data-end="1237">解除隐藏的图片上传 <code data-start="1185" data-end="1213">&lt;input id="upload-photos"&gt;</code>，<code data-start="1214" data-end="1225">send_keys</code> 上传该页 PNG；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1240" data-end="1367">
<p data-start="1243" data-end="1367">找到 <code data-start="1246" data-end="1265">#prompt-text-area</code>（ProseMirror 区域），输入预设的中文提示：<br data-start="1292" data-end="1295">
“这张截图里的内容是什么意思？请面向初学者详细解释，分点讲清楚。”<br data-start="1333" data-end="1336">
然后回车提交（若站点不响应，就点发送按钮兜底）；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1370" data-end="1399">
<p data-start="1373" data-end="1399">等待页面出现<strong data-start="1379" data-end="1391">最新一条助手回复</strong>，抓取文本；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1402" data-end="1460">
<p data-start="1405" data-end="1460">把“页图 + 提问 + 回答”<strong data-start="1420" data-end="1428">追加写入</strong>到 <code data-start="1430" data-end="1447">output/notes.md</code>，图片用相对路径引用。</p>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ul>
<blockquote data-start="1462" data-end="1530">
<p data-start="1464" data-end="1530">如果站点的 DOM 或提交流程稍有不同，只需要改 <code data-start="1489" data-end="1500">SELECTORS</code> 里的选择器，或者把提交逻辑从“回车发送”改成“点击按钮”。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="1532" data-end="1535">
<h2 data-start="1537" data-end="1545">常见调整点</h2>
<ul data-start="1547" data-end="1768">
<li data-start="1547" data-end="1627">
<p data-start="1549" data-end="1627"><strong data-start="1549" data-end="1561">只打开一次浏览器</strong>：默认 <code data-start="1565" data-end="1585">reuse_session=True</code>，整份 PDF 共用一个会话，更快；如果你希望每页都刷新页面，改成 <code data-start="1619" data-end="1626">False</code>。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1628" data-end="1675">
<p data-start="1630" data-end="1675"><strong data-start="1630" data-end="1638">超时时间</strong>：站点慢的话，调大 <code data-start="1648" data-end="1664">answer_timeout</code>（默认 120 秒）。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1676" data-end="1714">
<p data-start="1678" data-end="1714"><strong data-start="1678" data-end="1686">无头模式</strong>：把 <code data-start="1689" data-end="1704">headless=True</code> 就不弹浏览器窗口。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1715" data-end="1768">
<p data-start="1717" data-end="1768"><strong data-start="1717" data-end="1724">提示词</strong>：改 <code data-start="1727" data-end="1740">prompt_text</code> 可以替换成你的固定问题（比如“什么意思 详细解释”）。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1770" data-end="1773">
<p data-start="1775" data-end="1933" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">如果你把一个<strong data-start="1781" data-end="1795">目录里的多份 PDF</strong>都要处理，也可以在这个脚本的 <code data-start="1810" <p data-start="378" data-end="472">你给的 key（<code data-start="386" data-end="439">sk-fi9uVjhlfirEQMJRE8Da97D764624a948fC2B2657b58636e</code>）可以直接粘到 <code data-start="447" data-end="459">access_key</code>。建议私下保存，避免泄露。</p>

4.04235 18.0962 4.40306 18.1289 4.80371C18.1657 5.25395 18.165 5.81091 18.165 6.5V9.33301Z"></path></svg>复制代码</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">upload_image</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">driver: webdriver.Chrome, img_path: Path</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># The input is hidden; unhide via JS and send_keys</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        file_input = wait_for(driver, SELECTORS.FILE_INPUT, CFG.upload_timeout)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> TimeoutException:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">raise</span></span><span> TimeoutException(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"找不到文件上传 input#upload-photos。请检查选择器 SELECTORS.FILE_INPUT"</span></span><span>)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># Unhide</span></span><span>
    driver.execute_script(
        </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"arguments[0].className='';arguments[0].removeAttribute('aria-hidden');arguments[0].style=''"</span></span><span>,
        file_input,
    )
    file_input.send_keys(</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span>(img_path.resolve()))

    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ✅ 新增固定等待，确保上传完成</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"    等待上传完成中（10秒）..."</span></span><span>)
    time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">10</span></span><span>)
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="868" data-end="871">
<h3 data-start="873" data-end="886">💡 这样做的效果</h3>
<p data-start="887" data-end="899">每次执行到上传截图步骤：</p>
<ol data-start="900" data-end="992">
<li data-start="900" data-end="920">
<p data-start="903" data-end="920">脚本先解除隐藏 input 元素；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="921" data-end="945">
<p data-start="924" data-end="945">用 <code data-start="926" data-end="939">send_keys()</code> 上传图片；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="946" data-end="975">
<p data-start="949" data-end="975"><strong data-start="949" data-end="960">等待 10 秒</strong> 确保上传在服务器端完全结束；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="976" data-end="992">
<p data-start="979" data-end="992">然后再执行输入提问和发送。</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="994" data-end="997">
<p data-start="999" data-end="1052">如果你希望让等待时间可配置（写在配置区方便调整），也可以加一个配置项，比如在 <code data-start="1038" data-end="1046">Config</code> 类里增加：</p>

class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span>wait_for_upload_complete(driver, before, CFG.upload_timeout)
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
</li>
<li data-start="486" data-end="662">
<p data-start="488" data-end="548"><code data-start="488" data-end="514">wait_for_upload_complete</code> 会在超时前循环查找以下任意一种出现即可视为“上传完成并生成预览”：</p>
<ul data-start="551" data-end="662">
<li data-start="551" data-end="618">
<p data-start="553" data-end="618"><code data-start="553" data-end="586">span[style*="background-image"]</code>，且 <code data-start="589" data-end="596">style</code> 中包含 <code data-start="601" data-end="608">data:</code> 或 <code data-start="611" data-end="618">blob:</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="621" data-end="662">
<p data-start="623" data-end="662"><code data-start="623" data-end="642">img[src^="blob:"]</code>、<code data-start="643" data-end="662">img[src^="data:"]</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="663" data-end="696">
<p data-start="665" data-end="696">一旦检测到新 tile 或上述特征，即认为上传完成，进入提问。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="698" data-end="749">你在开发者工具里看到的<strong data-start="709" data-end="734">蓝色大段 <code data-start="716" data-end="732">data:image/...</code></strong> 正是我们现在用来判断的信号。</p>
<hr data-start="751" data-end="754">
<h2 data-start="756" data-end="767">你可以调整的参数</h2>
<p data-start="768" data-end="782">脚本顶部 <code data-start="773" data-end="781">CONFIG</code>：</p>
<ul data-start="783" data-end="887">
<li data-start="783" data-end="821">
<p data-start="785" data-end="821"><code data-start="785" data-end="801">upload_timeout</code>：等待上传预览的最大秒数（默认 60）。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="822" data-end="887">
<p data-start="824" data-end="887">其余配置（<code data-start="829" data-end="841">access_key</code>、<code data-start="842" data-end="855">prompt_text</code>、<code data-start="856" data-end="866">headless</code>、<code data-start="867" data-end="879">render_dpi</code> 等）保持不变。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="889" data-end="892">
<p data-start="894" data-end="1083" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">如果后面你发现站点把预览从 <code data-start="908" data-end="915">data:</code> 改成了 <code data-start="920" data-end="927">blob:</code> 或者 DOM 结构又换了，只需要改 <code data-start="946" data-end="980">SELECTORS.UPLOAD_TILE_CANDIDATES</code> 的 CSS 选择器即可。要不要我顺手再加一个<strong data-start="1003" data-end="1012">小日志打印</strong>（比如每 0.3s 打印一次已检测的缩略图数量），方便你观察？ <span class="align-middle" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="正在编码引语" class="rounded-xl px-1 bg-token-interactive-bg-tertiary-press text-token-text-secondary <h3 data-start="186" data-end="196">这版做了什么</h3>
<ul data-start="197" data-end="663">
<li data-start="197" data-end="314">
<p data-start="199" data-end="215"><strong data-start="199" data-end="213">清理上一次残留的附件</strong></p>
<ul data-start="218" data-end="314">
<li data-start="218" data-end="314">
<p data-start="220" data-end="314"><code data-start="220" data-end="241">clear_attachments()</code> 先尝试点击每个预览上的关闭按钮（常见是小“X”），点不到就用 JS 把预览节点移除并清空 <code data-start="287" data-end="303">#upload-photos</code> 的 <code data-start="306" data-end="313">value</code>。</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="315" data-end="554">
<p data-start="317" data-end="334"><strong data-start="317" data-end="332">等待上传完成 &amp; 稳定</strong></p>
<ul data-start="337" data-end="554">
<li data-start="337" data-end="437">
<p data-start="339" data-end="437"><code data-start="339" data-end="378">wait_stable_tile_count(..., expect=1)</code> 直到检测到<strong data-start="384" data-end="394">恰好 1 个</strong>预览缩略图，且在 <code data-start="403" data-end="417">stable_pause</code>（默认 0.8s）内数量不再变化才继续。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="440" data-end="554">
<p data-start="442" data-end="554">通过选择器抓 <code data-start="449" data-end="482">span[style*="background-image"]</code> 以及 <code data-start="486" data-end="513">img[src^="blob:"|"data:"]</code>，与你在 DevTools 里看到的蓝色 <code data-start="534" data-end="550">data:image/...</code> 一致。</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="555" data-end="663">
<p data-start="557" data-end="570"><strong data-start="557" data-end="568">发送后安全清空</strong></p>
<ul data-start="573" data-end="663">
<li data-start="573" data-end="663">
<p data-start="575" data-end="663">某些 UI 会把预览留到下一条消息，这里在 <code data-start="597" data-end="621">type_prompt_and_send()</code> 发送后再调用一次 <code data-start="631" data-end="652">clear_attachments()</code>，确保下一轮是干净的。</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="665" data-end="691">你可调整的参数（脚本顶部 <code data-start="682" data-end="690">CONFIG</code>）</h3>
<ul data-start="692" data-end="830">
<li data-start="692" data-end="729">
<p data-start="694" data-end="729"><code data-start="694" data-end="710">upload_timeout</code>：等待上传完成的最大秒数（默认 90）</p>
</li>
<li data-start="730" data-end="772">
<p data-start="732" data-end="772"><code data-start="732" data-end="746">stable_pause</code>：预览数量在该时长内不变才视为稳定（默认 0.8s）</p>
</li>
<li data-start="773" data-end="830">
<p data-start="775" data-end="830">其他：<code data-start="778" data-end="790">access_key</code>、<code data-start="791" data-end="804">prompt_text</code>、<code data-start="805" data-end="815">headless</code>、<code data-start="816" data-end="828">render_dpi</code> 等</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="832" data-end="980" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">如果站点后续变更了预览 DOM，只要改 <code data-start="852" data-end="886">SELECTORS.UPLOAD_TILE_CANDIDATES</code> 里的 CSS 选择器即可。<br data-start="900" data-end="903">
需要我再加<strong data-start="908" data-end="916">调试日志</strong>（如打印“预览计数变化：0→1”）方便你观察吗？ <span class="align-middle" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="正在编码引语" class="rounded-xl px-1 @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[72rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn" tabindex="-1"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div class="absolute flex h-8 w-3 origin-center items-center justify-center" style="opacity: 0; transform: origin-top-left flex-col gap-2 overflow-x-clip" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="" data-state="closed"><div class="relative w-full text-start"><div class="flex w-full items-start justify-between text-start flex-col"><button class="flex w-full items-center gap-0.5"><span class=""><span class="flex items-center gap-1 text-start align-middle truncate text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary" style="opacity: 1;">已思考 16s</span></span></button></div></div></span></div></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="af6b3727-b911-4e6d-8b6c-fea12f271440" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-thinking"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="97">看到了：第二轮开始会把<strong data-start="11" data-end="27">上一页的缩略图也一起带上</strong>，而且 UI 不继续往下走。根因是站点把上一轮的预览保留在<strong data-start="56" data-end="66">同一个输入区</strong>里，导致我们上传第二张时，预览变成了 2 张，随后就“卡住”。</p>
<p data-start="99" data-end="116">我已把脚本再强化了一版，做到三点：</p>
<ol data-start="118" data-end="324">
<li data-start="118" data-end="212">
<p data-start="121" data-end="212"><strong data-start="121" data-end="129">严格清空</strong>：每轮开始先在<strong data-start="136" data-end="152">Composer 表单内</strong>清空所有附件（点击每个缩略图的小“X”；点不到就用 JS 移除），并把 <code data-start="188" data-end="204">#upload-photos</code> 的值清空。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="213" data-end="267">
<p data-start="216" data-end="267"><strong data-start="216" data-end="229">只等 1 张且稳定</strong>：上传后等待<strong data-start="235" data-end="250">预览数=1 且持续稳定</strong>（默认 0.8s），才会发送。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="268" data-end="324">
<p data-start="271" data-end="324"><strong data-start="271" data-end="283">发送后再确保归零</strong>：发送完后等待预览数回到 0；如果 UI 不自动清空，再强制清空，避免下一轮叠加。</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="326" data-end="401"><strong data-start="326" data-end="338">下载最新版脚本：</strong><br data-start="338" data-end="341">
<span class="" data-state="closed"><a data-start="341" data-end="401" class="cursor-pointer">auto_qa_from_pdf.py</a></span></p>
<h3 data-start="403" data-end="421">技术要点（这版与之前的差异）</h3>
<ul data-start="422" data-end="874">
<li data-start="422" data-end="510">
<p data-start="424" data-end="510">预览缩略图全部<strong data-start="431" data-end="451">限定在 Composer 容器里</strong>查找：<code data-start="454" data-end="490">form[data-type='unified-composer']</code> 作为作用域，避免误抓历史消息中的图片。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="511" data-end="710">
<p data-start="513" data-end="523">计数/清空 API：</p>
<ul data-start="526" data-end="710">
<li data-start="526" data-end="628">
<p data-start="528" data-end="628"><code data-start="528" data-end="555">count_tiles_in_composer()</code>：只数输入区的 <code data-start="563" data-end="628">span[style*=background-image], img[src^=blob:], img[src^=data:]</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="631" data-end="710">
<p data-start="633" data-end="710"><code data-start="633" data-end="654">clear_attachments()</code>：先尝试点“关闭/删除/移除”等按钮；不成功则 <code data-start="678" data-end="688">remove()</code> 这些节点，并 <code data-start="696" data-end="710">inp.value=''</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="711" data-end="874">
<p data-start="713" data-end="718">发送逻辑：</p>
<ul data-start="721" data-end="874">
<li data-start="721" data-end="778">
<p data-start="723" data-end="778"><code data-start="723" data-end="739">upload_image()</code> → <code data-start="742" data-end="776">wait_stable_tile_count(expect=1)</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="781" data-end="874">
<p data-start="783" data-end="874"><code data-start="783" data-end="807">type_prompt_and_send()</code> 发送后 → <code data-start="814" data-end="848">wait_stable_tile_count(expect=0)</code>，超时再 <code data-start="853" data-end="874">clear_attachments()</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="876" data-end="1150" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">如果你那边的“X”按钮用的是别的 aria-label/title 文案（例如英文 Close/Remove），可以把 <code data-start="936" data-end="962">SELECTORS.TILE_CLOSE_SEL</code> 的选择器里再加上 <code data-start="972" data-end="1055">"button[aria-label*='close'],button[title*='close'],button[aria-label*='remove']"</code> 等关键字。<br data-start="1061" data-end="1064">

data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT 说：</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[72rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn" tabindex="-1"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="9ca4d39e-8d8b-462e-ba7c-18083e01b8b7" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-thinking"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="65">收到，你这条报错说明第二轮上传时<strong data-start="16" data-end="29">预览计数一直是 2</strong>，也就是上一轮的缩略图仍在输入区里。为此我做了两步保险处理并已写入脚本：</p>
<ol data-start="67" data-end="346">
<li data-start="67" data-end="172">
<p data-start="70" data-end="172"><strong data-start="70" data-end="88">每一页都刷新到干净的输入界面</strong>（默认 <code data-start="92" data-end="113">reuse_session=False</code>）<br data-start="114" data-end="117">
在每轮开始前都会 <code data-start="129" data-end="149">go_to_chat(driver)</code>，这样就相当于新开一轮对话，避免旧缩略图残留。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="174" data-end="346">
<p data-start="177" data-end="221"><strong data-start="177" data-end="210">上传后如果仍出现多于 1 张预览，强制清空并仅重试一次上传</strong><br data-start="210" data-end="213">
逻辑：</p>
<ul data-start="225" data-end="346">
<li data-start="225" data-end="243">
<p data-start="227" data-end="243">期待 <code data-start="230" data-end="240">count==1</code>；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="247" data-end="315">
<p data-start="249" data-end="315">如果 <code data-start="252" data-end="261">count&gt;1</code>，立刻 <code data-start="265" data-end="286">clear_attachments()</code>（只清输入区），然后重新 <code data-start="299" data-end="312">send_keys()</code>；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="319" data-end="346">
<p data-start="321" data-end="346">若重试后还是 <code data-start="328" data-end="332">&gt;1</code>，抛错提醒（防止无限等待）。</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="348" data-end="356">另外依然保留了：</p>
<ul data-start="357" data-end="456">
<li data-start="357" data-end="376">
<p data-start="359" data-end="376">上传前<strong data-start="362" data-end="373">清空输入区预览</strong>；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="377" data-end="406">
<p data-start="379" data-end="406">发送后<strong data-start="382" data-end="394">等待预览回到 0</strong>（不行就强制清空）；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="407" data-end="456">
<p data-start="409" data-end="456">预览计数和清理都只在 <strong data-start="420" data-end="435">Composer 表单</strong> 作用域内进行，避免误数历史消息里的图片。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="458" data-end="533"><strong data-start="458" data-end="470">下载更新版脚本：</strong><br data-start="470" data-end="473">
<span class="" data-state="closed"><a data-start="473" data-end="533" class="cursor-pointer">auto_qa_from_pdf.py</a></span></p>
<h3 data-start="535" data-end="547">你需要做的两件事</h3>
<ul data-start="548" data-end="639">
<li data-start="548" data-end="588">
<p data-start="550" data-end="588">把 <code data-start="552" data-end="560">Config</code> 里的 <code data-start="564" data-end="576">access_key</code> 改成你的 key；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="589" data-end="639">
<p data-start="591" data-end="639">直接运行：<code data-start="596" data-end="624">python auto_qa_from_pdf.py</code>（现在默认每轮都会刷新页面）。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="641" data-end="729">如果你想在一个会话里反复提问再切页，把 <code data-start="661" data-end="681">reuse_session=True</code> 也行，但这个站点的输入区会留下上一次的预览，我建议先用默认的 <strong data-start="713" data-end="721">每轮刷新</strong> 方案更稳。</p>
<p data-start="731" data-end="872" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">如果仍然出现 “当前=2”，我可以加<strong data-start="749" data-end="757">调试打印</strong>（每 200ms 输出一次预览数量变化），或者你把控制台截图/页面 DOM data-end="9">
你无法“下载”主要是因为在这个对话环境中，下载链接其实是“沙盒路径”，并不会直接打开。<br data-start="52" data-end="55">
下面有三种可靠的获取方法：</p>
<hr data-start="70" data-end="73">
<h3 data-start="75" data-end="97">✅ 方法 1：直接点“下载文件”按钮</h3>
<p data-start="98" data-end="115">在我上条消息里，你应该能看到一行：</p>
<blockquote data-start="117" data-end="179">
<p data-start="119" data-end="179"><span class="" data-state="closed"><a data-start="119" data-end="179" class="cursor-pointer">auto_qa_from_pdf.py</a></span></p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="181" data-end="235">👉 请<strong data-start="185" data-end="199">点击这个蓝色文字链接</strong>，系统会自动下载文件到你的电脑（通常会弹出保存框或直接保存到下载目录）。</p>
<hr data-start="237" data-end="240">
<h3 data-start="242" data-end="260">✅ 方法 2：如果点击无反应</h3>
<p data-start="261" data-end="330">右键这个链接 → 选择 <strong data-start="273" data-end="287">“链接另存为...”</strong><br data-start="287" data-end="290">
保存文件名为 <code data-start="297" data-end="318">auto_qa_from_pdf.py</code>，放到你本地的项目目录。</p>
<hr data-start="332" data-end="335">
<h3 data-start="337" data-end="361">✅ 方法 3：我可以直接输出完整脚本文本</h3>
<p data-start="362" data-end="430">如果你希望我直接把脚本的完整内容贴出来（方便你复制进 <code data-start="389" data-end="394">.py</code> 文件），<br data-start="399" data-end="402">
你回复一句 <strong data-start="408" data-end="419">“直接贴代码”</strong> 我就完整展开发给你。</p>
<hr data-start="432" data-end="435">
<p data-start="437" data-end="482" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">我建议你先试试方法 1 或 2。<br data-start="453" data-end="456">
确认能下载了吗？如果还不行，我就直接贴脚本源码给你。</p></div></div></div></div><div class="flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="76">明白，你需要<strong data-start="6" data-end="19">同一个会话连续提问</strong>，不能刷新成新聊天。我已经把脚本改回“<strong data-start="38" data-end="45">不刷新</strong>”模式，并保留了“只带一张图 &amp; 上传完成再发送”的防抖逻辑。</p>

<h3 data-start="155" data-end="164">现在的行为</h3>
<ul data-start="165" data-end="341">
<li data-start="165" data-end="224">
<p data-start="167" data-end="224"><code data-start="167" data-end="187">reuse_session=True</code>（默认）：不会在第二问开始前刷新页面，始终在<strong data-start="209" data-end="218">同一个聊天</strong>里连续发问。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="225" data-end="291">
<p data-start="227" data-end="291">每轮开始先<strong data-start="232" data-end="245">清空输入区的缩略图</strong>；上传后等待<strong data-start="251" data-end="264">预览==1 且稳定</strong>再发送；发送后再确保<strong data-start="274" data-end="282">预览归零</strong>，避免下一轮叠加。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="292" data-end="341">
<p data-start="294" data-end="341">若出现“上传后预览&gt;1”的异常：脚本会<strong data-start="313" data-end="328">强制清空并重试一次上传</strong>；仍异常才报错，防止死等。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="343" data-end="480" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">如果你仍遇到第二问出现两张图，发我一张<strong data-start="362" data-end="382">输入区预览缩略图的 DOM 结构</strong>（展开到包含“×”按钮的那层），我就把清理选择器再<strong data-start="407" data-end="415">精确对位</strong>到该站点的真实节点，保证 0→1→0 的流程稳定。 <span class="align-middle" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="正在编码引语" class="rounded-xl px-1 <p data-start="320" data-end="351">修改脚本顶部配置区，把你的 key、PDF 路径等改成自己的。</p>

class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span><span class="hljs-comment">#!/usr/bin/env python3</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># -*- coding: utf-8 -*-</span></span><span>
<span class="hljs-string">"""
Auto Q&amp;A from PDF pages into a web chat (Selenium) and Markdown notes.

✅ 支持：
- 进入页面自动输入 key 登录；
- 上传 PDF 每页截图；
- 确认上传完成后提问；
- 每次只附带一张图片；
- 不刷新页面，保持同一聊天会话；
- 输出 Markdown 备课笔记（含图片和回答）。
"""</span>

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> __future__ </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> annotations
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> sys, time, shutil
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> dataclasses </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> dataclass
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> pathlib </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> Path
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> typing </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-type">List</span></span><span>, </span><span><span class="hljs-type">Optional</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> fitz  </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># PyMuPDF</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> webdriver
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium.webdriver.common.by </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> By
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium.webdriver.common.keys </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> Keys
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium.webdriver.chrome.service </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> Service </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">as</span></span><span> ChromeService
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium.webdriver.chrome.options </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> Options </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">as</span></span><span> ChromeOptions
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> webdriver_manager.chrome </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> ChromeDriverManager
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium.webdriver.support.ui </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> WebDriverWait
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium.webdriver.support </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> expected_conditions </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">as</span></span><span> EC
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium.common.exceptions </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> TimeoutException, NoSuchElementException, ElementNotInteractableException

</span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ===================== CONFIG =====================</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-meta">@dataclass</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title class_">Config</span></span><span>:
    input_pdf: Path = Path(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"input.pdf"</span></span><span>)  </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 你的 PDF 文件路径</span></span><span>
    out_dir: Path = Path(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"output"</span></span><span>)
    site_url: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"https://dn7vxt.aitianhu2.top/?model=gpt-5"</span></span><span>
    login_url: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"https://dn7vxt.aitianhu2.top/list"</span></span><span>
    access_key: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"在这里填入你的 key"</span></span><span>
    prompt_text: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"这张截图里的内容是什么意思？请面向初学者详细解释，分点讲清楚。"</span></span><span>
    reuse_session: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">bool</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>       </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ✅ 保持同一个聊天，不刷新页面</span></span><span>
    headless: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">bool</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">False</span></span><span>
    page_load_timeout: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">30</span></span><span>
    upload_timeout: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">90</span></span><span>
    answer_timeout: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">120</span></span><span>
    post_submit_sleep: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">float</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">1.2</span></span><span>
    render_dpi: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">180</span></span><span>
    stable_pause: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">float</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.8</span></span><span>

CFG = Config()

</span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ===================== SELECTORS =====================</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title class_">SELECTORS</span></span><span>:
    KEY_INPUT = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"input#input-code"</span></span><span>)
    LOGIN_BUTTON = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"button#login-button"</span></span><span>)
    FILE_INPUT = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"input#upload-photos[type='file']"</span></span><span>)
    PROMPT_AREA = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"div#prompt-text-area[contenteditable='true']"</span></span><span>)
    PROMPT_AREA_FALLBACK = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"div.ProseMirror[contenteditable='true']"</span></span><span>)
    SEND_BUTTON = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"button[data-testid='composer-trailing-action']"</span></span><span>)
    ASSISTANT_MESSAGE = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"[data-message-author-role='assistant'], div.assistant, div.markdown"</span></span><span>)
    COMPOSER_FORM = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"form[data-type='unified-composer']"</span></span><span>)
    TILE_SEL = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"span[style*='background-image'],img[src^='blob:'],img[src^='data:']"</span></span><span>
    TILE_CLOSE_SEL = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"button[aria-label*='删'],button[aria-label*='移除'],button[aria-label*='关闭'],button[aria-label*='取消']"</span></span><span>

</span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ===================== UTILITIES =====================</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">ensure_out_dirs</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">base: Path</span></span><span>):
    images_dir = base / </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"pages"</span></span><span>
    assets_dir = base / </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"notes_assets"</span></span><span>
    base.mkdir(parents=</span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>, exist_ok=</span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>)
    images_dir.mkdir(exist_ok=</span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>)
    assets_dir.mkdir(exist_ok=</span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> images_dir, assets_dir

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">pdf_to_images</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">pdf_path: Path, images_dir: Path, dpi: <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">180</span></span><span>):
    doc = fitz.</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">open</span></span><span>(pdf_path)
    image_paths = []
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span></span><span> i, page </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">in</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">enumerate</span></span><span>(doc, start=</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>):
        pix = page.get_pixmap(matrix=fitz.Matrix(dpi/</span><span><span class="hljs-number">72</span></span><span>, dpi/</span><span><span class="hljs-number">72</span></span><span>))
        out_path = images_dir / </span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"page-<span class="hljs-subst">{i:03d}</span></span></span><span>.png"
        pix.save(</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span>(out_path))
        image_paths.append(out_path)
    doc.close()
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> image_paths

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">start_browser</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">headless=<span class="hljs-literal">False</span></span></span><span>):
    options = ChromeOptions()
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> headless:
        options.add_argument(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"--headless=new"</span></span><span>)
    options.add_argument(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"--disable-gpu"</span></span><span>)
    options.add_argument(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"--no-sandbox"</span></span><span>)
    options.add_argument(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"--window-size=1400,900"</span></span><span>)
    driver = webdriver.Chrome(service=ChromeService(ChromeDriverManager().install()), options=options)
    driver.set_page_load_timeout(CFG.page_load_timeout)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> driver

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">wait_for</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">driver, selector, timeout</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> WebDriverWait(driver, timeout).until(EC.presence_of_element_located(selector))

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">maybe_login</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">driver</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        key_input = WebDriverWait(driver, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">3</span></span><span>).until(EC.presence_of_element_located(SELECTORS.KEY_INPUT))
        key_input.clear()
        key_input.send_keys(CFG.access_key)
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
            driver.find_element(*SELECTORS.LOGIN_BUTTON).click()
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> NoSuchElementException:
            key_input.send_keys(Keys.ENTER)
        time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> TimeoutException:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span></span><span>

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">go_to_chat</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">driver</span></span><span>):
    driver.get(CFG.login_url)
    maybe_login(driver)
    driver.get(CFG.site_url)
    maybe_login(driver)
    time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.6</span></span><span>)

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">get_composer</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">driver</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> wait_for(driver, SELECTORS.COMPOSER_FORM, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">10</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> TimeoutException:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> driver.find_element(By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"body"</span></span><span>)

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">count_tiles</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">driver</span></span><span>):
    composer = get_composer(driver)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span><span>(driver.execute_script(
        </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"return arguments[0].querySelectorAll(arguments[1]).length;"</span></span><span>, composer, SELECTORS.TILE_SEL))

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">clear_attachments</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">driver, timeout=<span class="hljs-number">5.0</span></span></span><span>):
    composer = get_composer(driver)
    end = time.time() + timeout
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span></span><span> time.time() &lt; end:
        cnt = count_tiles(driver)
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> cnt == </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">break</span></span><span>
        driver.execute_script(<span class="hljs-string">"""
            const root = arguments[0];
            root.querySelectorAll(arguments[1]).forEach(el=&gt;el.remove());
            const inp = root.querySelector("input#upload-photos[type='file']") || document.querySelector("input#upload-photos[type='file']");
            if (inp) inp.value='';
        """</span>, composer, SELECTORS.TILE_SEL)
        time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.2</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> count_tiles(driver)

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">wait_stable_tile_count</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">driver, expect, stable_pause, overall_timeout</span></span><span>):
    end = time.time() + overall_timeout
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span></span><span> time.time() &lt; end:
        cnt = count_tiles(driver)
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> cnt == expect:
            t0 = time.time()
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span></span><span> time.time() - t0 &lt; stable_pause:
                </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> count_tiles(driver) != expect:
                    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">break</span></span><span>
                time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.1</span></span><span>)
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span></span><span>:
                </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span>
        time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.2</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">raise</span></span><span> TimeoutException(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"等待预览数量稳定为 <span class="hljs-subst">{expect}</span></span></span><span> 超时（当前=</span><span><span class="hljs-subst">{count_tiles(driver)}</span></span><span>）。")

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">upload_image</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">driver, img_path: Path</span></span><span>):
    clear_attachments(driver)
    file_input = wait_for(driver, SELECTORS.FILE_INPUT, CFG.upload_timeout)
    driver.execute_script(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"arguments[0].style='';"</span></span><span>, file_input)
    file_input.send_keys(</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span>(img_path.resolve()))
    wait_stable_tile_count(driver, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>, CFG.stable_pause, CFG.upload_timeout)

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">type_prompt_and_send</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">driver, text</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        prompt = wait_for(driver, SELECTORS.PROMPT_AREA, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">10</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> TimeoutException:
        prompt = wait_for(driver, SELECTORS.PROMPT_AREA_FALLBACK, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">5</span></span><span>)
    prompt.click()
    prompt.send_keys(text)
    prompt.send_keys(Keys.ENTER)
    time.sleep(CFG.post_submit_sleep)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        driver.find_element(*SELECTORS.SEND_BUTTON).click()
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> Exception:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        wait_stable_tile_count(driver, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>, CFG.stable_pause, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">10</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> TimeoutException:
        clear_attachments(driver)

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">wait_for_latest_answer</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">driver, timeout</span></span><span>):
    wait_for(driver, SELECTORS.ASSISTANT_MESSAGE, timeout)
    time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>)
    nodes = driver.find_elements(*SELECTORS.ASSISTANT_MESSAGE)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> nodes[-</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>].text.strip() </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> nodes </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">append_to_md</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">md_file: Path, rel_img: Path, answer: <span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span></span><span>, idx: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">with</span></span><span> md_file.</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">open</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"a"</span></span><span>, encoding=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"utf-8"</span></span><span>) </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">as</span></span><span> f:
        f.write(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"\n\n---\n\n## 第 <span class="hljs-subst">{idx}</span></span></span><span> 页\n\n")
        f.write(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"![第 <span class="hljs-subst">{idx}</span></span></span><span> 页](</span><span><span class="hljs-subst">{rel_img.as_posix()}</span></span><span>)\n\n")
        f.write(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"**提问：** <span class="hljs-subst">{CFG.prompt_text}</span></span></span><span>\n\n**回答：**\n\n</span><span><span class="hljs-subst">{answer}</span></span><span>\n")

</span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ===================== MAIN =====================</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">main</span></span><span>():
    images_dir, assets_dir = ensure_out_dirs(CFG.out_dir)
    notes_md = CFG.out_dir / </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"notes.md"</span></span><span>

    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">not</span></span><span> CFG.input_pdf.exists():
        </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"[ERROR] PDF 不存在：<span class="hljs-subst">{CFG.input_pdf}</span></span></span><span>")
        sys.exit(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">2</span></span><span>)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"[1/5] PDF → 图片"</span></span><span>)
    pages = pdf_to_images(CFG.input_pdf, images_dir, CFG.render_dpi)
    driver = start_browser(CFG.headless)
    go_to_chat(driver)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"[2/5] 登录并准备开始"</span></span><span>)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span></span><span> idx, img_path </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">in</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">enumerate</span></span><span>(pages, start=</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>):
        </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"  - 第 <span class="hljs-subst">{idx}</span></span></span><span> 页 </span><span><span class="hljs-subst">{img_path.name}</span></span><span>")
        target = assets_dir / img_path.name
        shutil.copy(img_path, target)
        rel = Path(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"notes_assets"</span></span><span>) / img_path.name
        upload_image(driver, target)
        type_prompt_and_send(driver, CFG.prompt_text)
        answer = wait_for_latest_answer(driver, CFG.answer_timeout)
        append_to_md(notes_md, rel, answer, idx)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"[✔] 完成！输出：<span class="hljs-subst">{notes_md.resolve()}</span></span></span><span>")
    driver.quit()

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> __name__ == </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"__main__"</span></span><span>:
    main()
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>

class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span><span class="hljs-comment">#!/usr/bin/env python3</span></span><span>

<span class="hljs-string">"""

✅ 支持：
- 自动输入 key 登录；
- 上传 PDF 每页截图；
- 确认上传完成后提问；
- 每次只附带一张图片；
- 不刷新页面，保持同一聊天会话；
- 输出 Markdown 备课笔记。
"""</span>

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> __future__ </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> annotations

    input_pdf: Path = Path(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"Week 11 - 2. Scalable Algorithm Templates.pdf"</span></span><span>)  </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ← 你的 PDF 文件名</span></span><span>
    out_dir: Path = Path(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"output"</span></span><span>)
    site_url: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"https://dn7vxt.aitianhu2.top/?model=gpt-5"</span></span><span>
    login_url: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"https://dn7vxt.aitianhu2.top/list"</span></span><span>
    access_key: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"sk-fi9uVjhlfirEQMJRE8Da97D764624a948fC2B2657b58636e"</span></span><span>  </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ← 你的 key</span></span><span>
    prompt_text: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"这张截图里的内容是什么意思？请面向初学者详细解释，分点讲清楚。"</span></span><span>
    reuse_session: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">bool</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>       </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ✅ 保持同一个聊天，不刷新页面</span></span><span>

    COMPOSER_FORM = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"form[data-type='unified-composer']"</span></span><span>)
    TILE_SEL = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"span[style*='background-image'],img[src^='blob:'],img[src^='data:']"</span></span><span>
    TILE_CLOSE_SEL = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"button[aria-label*='删'],button[aria-label*='移除'],button[aria-label*='关闭'],button[aria-label*='取消']"</span></span><span>

</span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ===================== UTILITIES =====================</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">ensure_out_dirs</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">base: Path</span></span><span>):
    images_dir = base / </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"pages"</span></span><span>
    assets_dir = base / </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"notes_assets"</span></span><span>
    base.mkdir(parents=</span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>, exist_ok=</span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>)
    images_dir.mkdir(exist_ok=</span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>)
    assets_dir.mkdir(exist_ok=</span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> images_dir, assets_dir

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">pdf_to_images</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">pdf_path: Path, images_dir: Path, dpi: <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">180</span></span><span>):
    doc = fitz.</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">open</span></span><span>(pdf_path)
    image_paths = []
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span></span><span> i, page </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">in</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">enumerate</span></span><span>(doc, start=</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>):
        pix = page.get_pixmap(matrix=fitz.Matrix(dpi/</span><span><span class="hljs-number">72</span></span><span>, dpi/</span><span><span class="hljs-number">72</span></span><span>))
        out_path = images_dir / </span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"page-<span class="hljs-subst">{i:03d}</span></span></span><span>.png"
        pix.save(</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span>(out_path))
        image_paths.append(out_path)
    doc.close()
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> image_paths

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">start_browser</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">headless=<span class="hljs-literal">False</span></span></span><span>):
    options = ChromeOptions()
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> headless:
        options.add_argument(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"--headless=new"</span></span><span>)
    options.add_argument(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"--disable-gpu"</span></span><span>)
    options.add_argument(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"--no-sandbox"</span></span><span>)
    options.add_argument(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"--window-size=1400,900"</span></span><span>)
    driver = webdriver.Chrome(service=ChromeService(ChromeDriverManager().install()), options=options)
    driver.set_page_load_timeout(CFG.page_load_timeout)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> driver

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">wait_for</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">driver, selector, timeout</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> WebDriverWait(driver, timeout).until(EC.presence_of_element_located(selector))

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">maybe_login</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">driver</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        key_input = WebDriverWait(driver, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">3</span></span><span>).until(EC.presence_of_element_located(SELECTORS.KEY_INPUT))
        key_input.clear()
        key_input.send_keys(CFG.access_key)
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
            driver.find_element(*SELECTORS.LOGIN_BUTTON).click()
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> NoSuchElementException:
            key_input.send_keys(Keys.ENTER)
        time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> TimeoutException:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span></span><span>

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">go_to_chat</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">driver</span></span><span>):
    driver.get(CFG.login_url)
    maybe_login(driver)
    driver.get(CFG.site_url)
    maybe_login(driver)
    time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.6</span></span><span>)

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">get_composer</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">driver</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> wait_for(driver, SELECTORS.COMPOSER_FORM, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">10</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> TimeoutException:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> driver.find_element(By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"body"</span></span><span>)

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">count_tiles</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">driver</span></span><span>):
    composer = get_composer(driver)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span><span>(driver.execute_script(
        </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"return arguments[0].querySelectorAll(arguments[1]).length;"</span></span><span>, composer, SELECTORS.TILE_SEL))

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">clear_attachments</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">driver, timeout=<span class="hljs-number">5.0</span></span></span><span>):
    composer = get_composer(driver)
    end = time.time() + timeout
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span></span><span> time.time() &lt; end:
        cnt = count_tiles(driver)
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> cnt == </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">break</span></span><span>
        driver.execute_script(<span class="hljs-string">"""
            const root = arguments[0];
            root.querySelectorAll(arguments[1]).forEach(el=&gt;el.remove());
            const inp = root.querySelector("input#upload-photos[type='file']") || document.querySelector("input#upload-photos[type='file']");
            if (inp) inp.value='';
        """</span>, composer, SELECTORS.TILE_SEL)
        time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.2</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> count_tiles(driver)

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">wait_stable_tile_count</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">driver, expect, stable_pause, overall_timeout</span></span><span>):
    end = time.time() + overall_timeout
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span></span><span> time.time() &lt; end:
        cnt = count_tiles(driver)
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> cnt == expect:
            t0 = time.time()
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span></span><span> time.time() - t0 &lt; stable_pause:
                </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> count_tiles(driver) != expect:
                    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">break</span></span><span>
                time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.1</span></span><span>)
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span></span><span>:
                </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span>
        time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.2</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">raise</span></span><span> TimeoutException(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"等待预览数量稳定为 <span class="hljs-subst">{expect}</span></span></span><span> 超时（当前=</span><span><span class="hljs-subst">{count_tiles(driver)}</span></span><span>）。")

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">upload_image</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">driver, img_path: Path</span></span><span>):
    clear_attachments(driver)
    file_input = wait_for(driver, SELECTORS.FILE_INPUT, CFG.upload_timeout)
    driver.execute_script(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"arguments[0].style='';"</span></span><span>, file_input)
    file_input.send_keys(</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span>(img_path.resolve()))
    wait_stable_tile_count(driver, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>, CFG.stable_pause, CFG.upload_timeout)

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">type_prompt_and_send</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">driver, text</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        prompt = wait_for(driver, SELECTORS.PROMPT_AREA, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">10</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> TimeoutException:
        prompt = wait_for(driver, SELECTORS.PROMPT_AREA_FALLBACK, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">5</span></span><span>)
    prompt.click()
    prompt.send_keys(text)
    prompt.send_keys(Keys.ENTER)
    time.sleep(CFG.post_submit_sleep)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        driver.find_element(*SELECTORS.SEND_BUTTON).click()
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> Exception:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        wait_stable_tile_count(driver, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>, CFG.stable_pause, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">10</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> TimeoutException:
        clear_attachments(driver)

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">wait_for_latest_answer</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">driver, timeout</span></span><span>):
    wait_for(driver, SELECTORS.ASSISTANT_MESSAGE, timeout)
    time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>)
    nodes = driver.find_elements(*SELECTORS.ASSISTANT_MESSAGE)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> nodes[-</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>].text.strip() </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> nodes </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">append_to_md</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">md_file: Path, rel_img: Path, answer: <span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span></span><span>, idx: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">with</span></span><span> md_file.</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">open</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"a"</span></span><span>, encoding=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"utf-8"</span></span><span>) </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">as</span></span><span> f:
        f.write(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"\n\n---\n\n## 第 <span class="hljs-subst">{idx}</span></span></span><span> 页\n\n")
        f.write(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"![第 <span class="hljs-subst">{idx}</span></span></span><span> 页](</span><span><span class="hljs-subst">{rel_img.as_posix()}</span></span><span>)\n\n")
        f.write(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"**提问：** <span class="hljs-subst">{CFG.prompt_text}</span></span></span><span>\n\n**回答：**\n\n</span><span><span class="hljs-subst">{answer}</span></span><span>\n")

</span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ===================== MAIN =====================</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">main</span></span><span>():
    images_dir, assets_dir = ensure_out_dirs(CFG.out_dir)
    notes_md = CFG.out_dir / </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"notes.md"</span></span><span>

    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">not</span></span><span> CFG.input_pdf.exists():
        </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"[ERROR] PDF 不存在：<span class="hljs-subst">{CFG.input_pdf}</span></span></span><span>")
        sys.exit(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">2</span></span><span>)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"[1/5] PDF → 图片"</span></span><span>)
    pages = pdf_to_images(CFG.input_pdf, images_dir, CFG.render_dpi)
    driver = start_browser(CFG.headless)
    go_to_chat(driver)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"[2/5] 登录并准备开始"</span></span><span>)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span></span><span> idx, img_path </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">in</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">enumerate</span></span><span>(pages, start=</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>):
        </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"  - 第 <span class="hljs-subst">{idx}</span></span></span><span> 页 </span><span><span class="hljs-subst">{img_path.name}</span></span><span>")
        target = assets_dir / img_path.name
        shutil.copy(img_path, target)
        rel = Path(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"notes_assets"</span></span><span>) / img_path.name
        upload_image(driver, target)
        type_prompt_and_send(driver, CFG.prompt_text)
        answer = wait_for_latest_answer(driver, CFG.answer_timeout)
        append_to_md(notes_md, rel, answer, idx)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"[✔] 完成！输出：<span class="hljs-subst">{notes_md.resolve()}</span></span></span><span>")
    driver.quit()

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> __name__ == </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"__main__"</span></span><span>:
    main()
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="8657" data-end="8660">
<p data-start="8662" data-end="8712">直接复制粘贴上面内容保存成 <code data-start="8676" data-end="8697">auto_qa_from_pdf.py</code> 就能用了。<br data-start="8703" data-end="8706">
运行时确保：</p>
<ul data-start="8713" data-end="8872">
<li data-start="8713" data-end="8798">
<p data-start="8715" data-end="8798">你的 PDF 文件名就是<br data-start="8727" data-end="8730">
<strong data-start="8732" data-end="8781">Week 11 - 2. Scalable Algorithm Templates.pdf</strong><br data-start="8781" data-end="8784">
并且和脚本在同一文件夹；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="8799" data-end="8819">
<p data-start="8801" data-end="8819">电脑上安装好 Chrome 浏览器；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="8820" data-end="8872">
<p data-start="8822" data-end="8827">终端运行：</p>

data-testid="conversation-turn-26" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant" style=""><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT 说：</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[72rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn" tabindex="-1"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="15e9e1ec-2e63-4eba-9de6-11f75db2ec9d" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="112">太好了，你提供的错误非常关键。<br data-start="15" data-end="18">
问题的根源是：<strong data-start="25" data-end="67">站点在同一会话里，发送完一条消息后，不会自动清除上一轮的缩略图 DOM 节点</strong>。<br data-start="68" data-end="71">
虽然你看不到第一张图在界面上“上传”，但它其实仍然保留在输入框的 DOM 里。</p>
<hr data-start="114" data-end="117">
<h2 data-start="119" data-end="127">🔍 根因</h2>
<p data-start="128" data-end="151">页面里的图片预览 DOM 没被自动移除，导致：</p>
<ul data-start="152" data-end="254">
<li data-start="152" data-end="196">
<p data-start="154" data-end="196">第二次上传时，<code data-start="161" data-end="182">input#upload-photos</code> 再次触发了 append；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="197" data-end="221">
<p data-start="199" data-end="221">结果预览区出现了 <strong data-start="208" data-end="220">两张图（旧+新）</strong>；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="222" data-end="254">
<p data-start="224" data-end="254">脚本检测到 <code data-start="230" data-end="248">count_tiles == 2</code> → 超时。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="256" data-end="259">
<h2 data-start="261" data-end="270">✅ 解决方案</h2>
<p data-start="271" data-end="337">我们强制在每轮上传前执行 <strong data-start="284" data-end="298">彻底的 DOM 清理</strong>：<br data-start="299" data-end="302">
直接删除整个预览容器元素（无论有没有“×”按钮），然后重建文件输入框。</p>
<p data-start="339" data-end="350">这个版本的核心修复点：</p>
<ol data-start="351" data-end="669">
<li data-start="351" data-end="621">
<p data-start="354" data-end="391">在 <code data-start="356" data-end="372">upload_image()</code> 最开始，执行 JavaScript：</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible!" data-start="395" data-end="621"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center
