class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span><span class="hljs-comment">#!/usr/bin/env python3</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># -*- coding: utf-8 -*-</span></span><span>
<span class="hljs-string">"""
Final Stable Version: Auto Q&amp;A from PDF pages into the web chat.

✅ 特点：
- 自动登录（使用 access_key）
- 不刷新页面，保持同一个聊天会话
- 每次提问只上传 1 张截图
- 上传前强制彻底清理旧图片 DOM
- 上传完成后检测稳定，再发送提问
- 自动生成 Markdown 备课文件
"""</span>

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> __future__ </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> annotations
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> sys, time, shutil
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> dataclasses </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> dataclass
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> pathlib </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> Path
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> fitz  </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># PyMuPDF</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> webdriver
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium.webdriver.common.by </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> By
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium.webdriver.common.keys </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> Keys
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium.webdriver.chrome.service </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> Service </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">as</span></span><span> ChromeService
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium.webdriver.chrome.options </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> Options </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">as</span></span><span> ChromeOptions
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> webdriver_manager.chrome </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> ChromeDriverManager
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium.webdriver.support.ui </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> WebDriverWait
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium.webdriver.support </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> expected_conditions </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">as</span></span><span> EC
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium.common.exceptions </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> TimeoutException, NoSuchElementException

</span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ===================== CONFIG =====================</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-meta">@dataclass</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title class_">Config</span></span><span>:
    input_pdf: Path = Path(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"Week 11 - 2. Scalable Algorithm Templates.pdf"</span></span><span>)
    out_dir: Path = Path(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"output"</span></span><span>)
    site_url: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"https://dn7vxt.aitianhu2.top/?model=gpt-5"</span></span><span>
    login_url: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"https://dn7vxt.aitianhu2.top/list"</span></span><span>
    access_key: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"sk-fi9uVjhlfirEQMJRE8Da97D764624a948fC2B2657b58636e"</span></span><span>
    prompt_text: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"这张截图里的内容是什么意思？请面向初学者详细解释，分点讲清楚。"</span></span><span>
    reuse_session: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">bool</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>
    headless: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">bool</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">False</span></span><span>
    page_load_timeout: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">30</span></span><span>
    upload_timeout: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">90</span></span><span>
    answer_timeout: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">120</span></span><span>
    post_submit_sleep: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">float</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">1.2</span></span><span>
    render_dpi: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">180</span></span><span>
    stable_pause: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">float</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.8</span></span><span>

CFG = Config()

</span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ===================== SELECTORS =====================</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title class_">SELECTORS</span></span><span>:
    KEY_INPUT = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"input#input-code"</span></span><span>)
    LOGIN_BUTTON = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"button#login-button"</span></span><span>)
    FILE_INPUT = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"input#upload-photos[type='file']"</span></span><span>)
    PROMPT_AREA = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"div#prompt-text-area[contenteditable='true']"</span></span><span>)
    PROMPT_AREA_FALLBACK = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"div.ProseMirror[contenteditable='true']"</span></span><span>)
    SEND_BUTTON = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"button[data-testid='composer-trailing-action']"</span></span><span>)
    ASSISTANT_MESSAGE = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"[data-message-author-role='assistant'], div.assistant, div.markdown"</span></span><span>)
    TILE_SEL = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"span[style*='background-image'],img[src^='blob:'],img[src^='data:']"</span></span><span>

</span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ===================== UTILITIES =====================</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">ensure_out_dirs</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">base: Path</span></span><span>):
    img_dir, asset_dir = base / </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"pages"</span></span><span>, base / </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"notes_assets"</span></span><span>
    base.mkdir(exist_ok=</span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>)
    img_dir.mkdir(exist_ok=</span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>)
    asset_dir.mkdir(exist_ok=</span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> img_dir, asset_dir

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">pdf_to_images</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">pdf_path: Path, out_dir: Path, dpi: <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">180</span></span><span>):
    doc = fitz.</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">open</span></span><span>(pdf_path)
    paths = []
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span></span><span> i, page </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">in</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">enumerate</span></span><span>(doc, start=</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>):
        pix = page.get_pixmap(matrix=fitz.Matrix(dpi/</span><span><span class="hljs-number">72</span></span><span>, dpi/</span><span><span class="hljs-number">72</span></span><span>))
        out_path = out_dir / </span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"page-<span class="hljs-subst">{i:03d}</span></span></span><span>.png"
        pix.save(out_path)
        paths.append(out_path)
    doc.close()
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> paths

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">start_browser</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">headless=<span class="hljs-literal">False</span></span></span><span>):
    opt = ChromeOptions()
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> headless:
        opt.add_argument(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"--headless=new"</span></span><span>)
    opt.add_argument(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"--disable-gpu"</span></span><span>)
    opt.add_argument(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"--no-sandbox"</span></span><span>)
    opt.add_argument(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"--window-size=1400,900"</span></span><span>)
    drv = webdriver.Chrome(service=ChromeService(ChromeDriverManager().install()), options=opt)
    drv.set_page_load_timeout(CFG.page_load_timeout)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> drv

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">wait_for</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, selector, timeout</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> WebDriverWait(drv, timeout).until(EC.presence_of_element_located(selector))

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">maybe_login</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        key_input = WebDriverWait(drv, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">3</span></span><span>).until(EC.presence_of_element_located(SELECTORS.KEY_INPUT))
        key_input.clear()
        key_input.send_keys(CFG.access_key)
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
            drv.find_element(*SELECTORS.LOGIN_BUTTON).click()
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> NoSuchElementException:
            key_input.send_keys(Keys.ENTER)
        time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> TimeoutException:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span></span><span>

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">go_to_chat</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv</span></span><span>):
    drv.get(CFG.login_url)
    maybe_login(drv)
    drv.get(CFG.site_url)
    maybe_login(drv)
    time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.5</span></span><span>)

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">clear_all_uploads</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"""彻底清理所有上传的预览 DOM 和文件输入值"""</span></span><span>
    drv.execute_script(<span class="hljs-string">"""
        document.querySelectorAll('span[style*="background-image"], img[src^="blob:"], img[src^="data:"]').forEach(el =&gt; el.remove());
        document.querySelectorAll('input#upload-photos').forEach(inp =&gt; inp.value = '');
    """</span>)
    time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.3</span></span><span>)

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">count_tiles</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> drv.execute_script(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"return document.querySelectorAll(arguments[0]).length;"</span></span><span>, SELECTORS.TILE_SEL)

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">wait_stable_tile_count</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, expect, timeout=<span class="hljs-number">60</span></span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"""等待缩略图数量稳定为目标值"""</span></span><span>
    end = time.time() + timeout
    last = -</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>
    stable_for = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span></span><span> time.time() &lt; end:
        cnt = count_tiles(drv)
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> cnt == expect:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> cnt == last:
                stable_for += </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.2</span></span><span>
                </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> stable_for &gt; CFG.stable_pause:
                    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span>
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span></span><span>:
                stable_for = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>
            last = cnt
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span></span><span>:
            stable_for = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>
            last = cnt
        time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.2</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">raise</span></span><span> TimeoutException(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"等待图片数量稳定为 <span class="hljs-subst">{expect}</span></span></span><span> 超时（当前=</span><span><span class="hljs-subst">{cnt}</span></span><span>）。")

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">upload_image</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, img_path: Path</span></span><span>):
    clear_all_uploads(drv)  </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ✅ 上传前彻底清理旧图片</span></span><span>
    file_input = wait_for(drv, SELECTORS.FILE_INPUT, CFG.upload_timeout)
    drv.execute_script(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"arguments[0].style='';"</span></span><span>, file_input)
    file_input.send_keys(</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span>(img_path.resolve()))
    wait_stable_tile_count(drv, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>, CFG.upload_timeout)

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">type_prompt_and_send</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, text</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        prompt = wait_for(drv, SELECTORS.PROMPT_AREA, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">10</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> TimeoutException:
        prompt = wait_for(drv, SELECTORS.PROMPT_AREA_FALLBACK, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">5</span></span><span>)
    prompt.click()
    prompt.send_keys(text)
    prompt.send_keys(Keys.ENTER)
    time.sleep(CFG.post_submit_sleep)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        drv.find_element(*SELECTORS.SEND_BUTTON).click()
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> Exception:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        wait_stable_tile_count(drv, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">10</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> TimeoutException:
        clear_all_uploads(drv)

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">wait_for_latest_answer</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, timeout</span></span><span>):
    wait_for(drv, SELECTORS.ASSISTANT_MESSAGE, timeout)
    time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>)
    nodes = drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.ASSISTANT_MESSAGE)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> nodes[-</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>].text.strip() </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> nodes </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">append_to_md</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">md_file, rel_img, answer, idx</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">with</span></span><span> md_file.</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">open</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"a"</span></span><span>, encoding=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"utf-8"</span></span><span>) </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">as</span></span><span> f:
        f.write(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"\n\n---\n\n## 第 <span class="hljs-subst">{idx}</span></span></span><span> 页\n\n")
        f.write(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"![第 <span class="hljs-subst">{idx}</span></span></span><span> 页](</span><span><span class="hljs-subst">{rel_img.as_posix()}</span></span><span>)\n\n")
        f.write(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"**提问：** <span class="hljs-subst">{CFG.prompt_text}</span></span></span><span>\n\n**回答：**\n\n</span><span><span class="hljs-subst">{answer}</span></span><span>\n")

</span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ===================== MAIN =====================</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">main</span></span><span>():
    img_dir, asset_dir = ensure_out_dirs(CFG.out_dir)
    notes_md = CFG.out_dir / </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"notes.md"</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">not</span></span><span> CFG.input_pdf.exists():
        </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"[ERROR] PDF 不存在：<span class="hljs-subst">{CFG.input_pdf}</span></span></span><span>")
        sys.exit(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">2</span></span><span>)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"[1/5] PDF → 图片"</span></span><span>)
    pages = pdf_to_images(CFG.input_pdf, img_dir, CFG.render_dpi)
    drv = start_browser(CFG.headless)
    go_to_chat(drv)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"[2/5] 登录成功，开始循环上传..."</span></span><span>)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span></span><span> idx, img_path </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">in</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">enumerate</span></span><span>(pages, start=</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>):
        </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"  - 处理第 <span class="hljs-subst">{idx}</span></span></span><span> 页：</span><span><span class="hljs-subst">{img_path.name}</span></span><span>")
        target = asset_dir / img_path.name
        shutil.copy(img_path, target)
        rel = Path(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"notes_assets"</span></span><span>) / img_path.name
        upload_image(drv, target)
        type_prompt_and_send(drv, CFG.prompt_text)
        answer = wait_for_latest_answer(drv, CFG.answer_timeout)
        append_to_md(notes_md, rel, answer, idx)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"[✔] 完成！结果保存在：<span class="hljs-subst">{notes_md.resolve()}</span></span></span><span>")
    drv.quit()

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> __name__ == </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"__main__"</span></span><span>:
    main()
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>

6.5V9.33301Z"></path></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div></article><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="d6024a75-e4ea-40cf-ae8d-275da01908bb" data-testid="conversation-turn-30" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant" style=""><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT 说：</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[72rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn" tabindex="-1"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div class="absolute flex h-8 w-3 origin-center items-center justify-center" style="opacity: 0; transform: scale(0);"><div class="bg-token-text-primary h-3 w-3 rounded-full"></div></div><div class="relative my-1 min-h-6"><div class="relative flex max-w-[calc(0.8*var(--thread-content-max-width,40rem))] origin-top-left flex-col gap-2 overflow-x-clip" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="" data-state="closed"><div class="relative w-full text-start"><div class="flex w-full items-start justify-between text-start flex-col"><button class="flex w-full items-center gap-0.5"><span class=""><span class="flex items-center gap-1 text-start align-middle truncate text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary" style="opacity: 1;">已思考 15s</span></span></button></div></div></span></div></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="6b70fb8b-e837-4fad-97ac-8a2066c8d5d9" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-thinking"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="242">好需求！你的站点在<strong data-start="9" data-end="20">模型还在生成时</strong>，发送区右侧的按钮是“■ 停止”样式（<code data-start="39" data-end="66">data-testid="stop-button"</code> / <code data-start="69" data-end="81">aria-label</code> 包含“停止生成”），等<strong data-start="93" data-end="103">完全生成结束</strong>才会变成“➤ 发送”（<code data-start="114" data-end="141">data-testid="send-button"</code>）。<br data-start="143" data-end="146">
解决思路：<strong data-start="151" data-end="173" data-is-only-node="">严禁在“停止按钮”存在时上传下一张图</strong>。我们新增一个 <code data-start="181" data-end="200">wait_until_idle()</code>，只要检测到“停止”按钮，就<strong data-start="214" data-end="232">阻塞等待直到按钮变回“发送”</strong>，再进行下一轮上传。</p>
<p data-start="244" data-end="282">下面给出<strong data-start="248" data-end="256">完整脚本</strong>（含你之前的 key 和 PDF 文件名），已集成：</p>
<ul data-start="284" data-end="389">
<li data-start="284" data-end="300">
<p data-start="286" data-end="300">不刷新会话、每轮只带一张图；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="301" data-end="318">
<p data-start="303" data-end="318">上传前强制清空旧预览 DOM；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="319" data-end="331">
<p data-start="321" data-end="331">等待上传稳定再发送；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="332" data-end="368">
<p data-start="334" data-end="368"><strong data-start="334" data-end="360">发送后等待回答彻底完成（“停止”→“发送”）</strong>，才进入下一轮；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="369" data-end="389">
<p data-start="371" data-end="389">仍生成 Markdown 备课文件。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="391" data-end="429">把下面代码保存为 <code data-start="400" data-end="421">auto_qa_from_pdf.py</code> 直接运行即可。</p>

class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span><span class="hljs-comment">#!/usr/bin/env python3</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># -*- coding: utf-8 -*-</span></span><span>
<span class="hljs-string">"""
Final Stable Version (with idle-wait):
- 同一会话连续提问
- 每次只上传 1 张图，上传前清理旧预览
- 回答未完成(存在 stop-button)时不进行下一轮
- 生成 Markdown 笔记
"""</span>

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> __future__ </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> annotations
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> sys, time, shutil
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> dataclasses </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> dataclass

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> fitz  </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># PyMuPDF</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> webdriver
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium.webdriver.common.by </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> By
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium.webdriver.common.keys </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> Keys
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium.webdriver.chrome.service </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> Service </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">as</span></span><span> ChromeService
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium.webdriver.chrome.options </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> Options </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">as</span></span><span> ChromeOptions
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> webdriver_manager.chrome </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> ChromeDriverManager
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium.webdriver.support.ui </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> WebDriverWait
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium.webdriver.support </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> expected_conditions </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">as</span></span><span> EC
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span></span><span> selenium.common.exceptions </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> TimeoutException, NoSuchElementException

</span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ===================== CONFIG =====================</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-meta">@dataclass</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title class_">Config</span></span><span>:
    input_pdf: Path = Path(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"Week 11 - 2. Scalable Algorithm Templates.pdf"</span></span><span>)
    out_dir: Path = Path(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"output"</span></span><span>)
    site_url: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"https://dn7vxt.aitianhu2.top/?model=gpt-5"</span></span><span>
    login_url: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"https://dn7vxt.aitianhu2.top/list"</span></span><span>
    access_key: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"sk-fi9uVjhlfirEQMJRE8Da97D764624a948fC2B2657b58636e"</span></span><span>
    prompt_text: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"这张截图里的内容是什么意思？请面向初学者详细解释，分点讲清楚。"</span></span><span>
    reuse_session: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">bool</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>
    headless: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">bool</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">False</span></span><span>
    page_load_timeout: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">30</span></span><span>
    upload_timeout: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">90</span></span><span>
    answer_timeout: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">120</span></span><span>
    post_submit_sleep: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">float</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">1.2</span></span><span>
    render_dpi: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">180</span></span><span>
    stable_pause: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">float</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.8</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 等待“生成完成”最大时长（等待 stop→send）</span></span><span>
    idle_timeout: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">180</span></span><span>

CFG = Config()

</span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ===================== SELECTORS =====================</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title class_">SELECTORS</span></span><span>:
    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 登录</span></span><span>
    KEY_INPUT = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"input#input-code"</span></span><span>)
    LOGIN_BUTTON = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"button#login-button"</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 发送区</span></span><span>
    FILE_INPUT = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"input#upload-photos[type='file']"</span></span><span>)
    PROMPT_AREA = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"div#prompt-text-area[contenteditable='true']"</span></span><span>)
    PROMPT_AREA_FALLBACK = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"div.ProseMirror[contenteditable='true']"</span></span><span>)
    SEND_BUTTON = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"button[data-testid='send-button'], button#composer-submit-button[aria-label*='发送']"</span></span><span>)
    STOP_BUTTON = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"button[data-testid='stop-button'], button#composer-submit-button[aria-label*='停止'], button[aria-label*='Stop']"</span></span><span>)
    ASSISTANT_MESSAGE = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"[data-message-author-role='assistant'], div.assistant, div.markdown"</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 预览缩略图（DOM 层面）</span></span><span>
    TILE_SEL = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"span[style*='background-image'],img[src^='blob:'],img[src^='data:']"</span></span><span>

</span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ===================== 工具函数 =====================</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">ensure_out_dirs</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">base: Path</span></span><span>):
    img_dir, asset_dir = base / </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"pages"</span></span><span>, base / </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"notes_assets"</span></span><span>
    base.mkdir(exist_ok=</span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>)
    img_dir.mkdir(exist_ok=</span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>)
    asset_dir.mkdir(exist_ok=</span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> img_dir, asset_dir

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">pdf_to_images</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">pdf_path: Path, out_dir: Path, dpi: <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">180</span></span><span>):
    doc = fitz.</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">open</span></span><span>(pdf_path)
    paths = []
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span></span><span> i, page </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">in</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">enumerate</span></span><span>(doc, start=</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>):
        pix = page.get_pixmap(matrix=fitz.Matrix(dpi/</span><span><span class="hljs-number">72</span></span><span>, dpi/</span><span><span class="hljs-number">72</span></span><span>))
        out_path = out_dir / </span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"page-<span class="hljs-subst">{i:03d}</span></span></span><span>.png"
        pix.save(out_path)
        paths.append(out_path)
    doc.close()
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> paths

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">start_browser</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">headless=<span class="hljs-literal">False</span></span></span><span>):
    opt = ChromeOptions()
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> headless:
        opt.add_argument(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"--headless=new"</span></span><span>)
    opt.add_argument(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"--disable-gpu"</span></span><span>); opt.add_argument(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"--no-sandbox"</span></span><span>)
    opt.add_argument(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"--window-size=1400,900"</span></span><span>)
    drv = webdriver.Chrome(service=ChromeService(ChromeDriverManager().install()), options=opt)
    drv.set_page_load_timeout(CFG.page_load_timeout)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> drv

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">wait_for</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, selector, timeout</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> WebDriverWait(drv, timeout).until(EC.presence_of_element_located(selector))

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">maybe_login</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        key_input = WebDriverWait(drv, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">3</span></span><span>).until(EC.presence_of_element_located(SELECTORS.KEY_INPUT))
        key_input.clear(); key_input.send_keys(CFG.access_key)
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
            drv.find_element(*SELECTORS.LOGIN_BUTTON).click()
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> NoSuchElementException:
            key_input.send_keys(Keys.ENTER)
        time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> TimeoutException:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span></span><span>

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">go_to_chat</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv</span></span><span>):
    drv.get(CFG.login_url); maybe_login(drv)
    drv.get(CFG.site_url);  maybe_login(drv)
    time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.5</span></span><span>)

</span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># —— 预览清理 &amp; 计数 ——</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">clear_all_uploads</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"""彻底清理所有上传预览 DOM 和文件输入值（不依赖 UI 的 × 按钮）"""</span></span><span>
    drv.execute_script(<span class="hljs-string">"""
        document.querySelectorAll('span[style*="background-image"], img[src^="blob:"], img[src^="data:"]').forEach(el =&gt; el.remove());
        document.querySelectorAll('input#upload-photos').forEach(inp =&gt; { try { inp.value = ''; } catch(e){} });
    """</span>)
    time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.3</span></span><span>)

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">count_tiles</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> drv.execute_script(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"return document.querySelectorAll(arguments[0]).length;"</span></span><span>, SELECTORS.TILE_SEL)

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">wait_stable_tile_count</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, expect, timeout=<span class="hljs-number">60</span></span></span><span>):
    end = time.time() + timeout
    last = -</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>; stable_for = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span></span><span> time.time() &lt; end:
        cnt = count_tiles(drv)
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> cnt == expect:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> cnt == last:
                stable_for += </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.2</span></span><span>
                </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> stable_for &gt; CFG.stable_pause:
                    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span>
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span></span><span>:
                stable_for = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>
            last = cnt
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span></span><span>:
            stable_for = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>; last = cnt
        time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.2</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">raise</span></span><span> TimeoutException(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"等待图片数量稳定为 <span class="hljs-subst">{expect}</span></span></span><span> 超时（当前=</span><span><span class="hljs-subst">{cnt}</span></span><span>）。")

</span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># —— 生成状态：等待 stop 按钮消失 / send 按钮出现 ——</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">is_generating</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv</span></span><span>) -&gt; </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">bool</span></span><span>:
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">len</span></span><span>(drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.STOP_BUTTON)) &gt; </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">wait_until_idle</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, timeout: <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"""等待模型生成完全结束：stop 按钮消失，send 按钮出现"""</span></span><span>
    end = time.time() + timeout
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span></span><span> time.time() &lt; end:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 生成中：看到 stop 按钮 → 继续等</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> is_generating(drv):
            time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.3</span></span><span>)
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">continue</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 没看到 stop，再确认 send 按钮已就绪</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">len</span></span><span>(drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.SEND_BUTTON)) &gt; </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span>
        time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.3</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">raise</span></span><span> TimeoutException(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"等待模型生成完成（stop→send）超时。"</span></span><span>)

</span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># —— 上传 / 发送 / 抓取 ——</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">upload_image</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, img_path: Path</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 防止上一轮生成未完成时误操作</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        wait_until_idle(drv, timeout=CFG.idle_timeout)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> TimeoutException:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 如果页面始终处于“生成中”，保险起见也继续清理+上传当前页</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span></span><span>

    clear_all_uploads(drv)  </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ✅ 上传前彻底清理旧图片</span></span><span>
    file_input = wait_for(drv, SELECTORS.FILE_INPUT, CFG.upload_timeout)
    drv.execute_script(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"arguments[0].style='';"</span></span><span>, file_input)
    file_input.send_keys(</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span>(img_path.resolve()))
    wait_stable_tile_count(drv, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>, CFG.upload_timeout)

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">type_prompt_and_send</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, text</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        prompt = wait_for(drv, SELECTORS.PROMPT_AREA, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">10</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> TimeoutException:
        prompt = wait_for(drv, SELECTORS.PROMPT_AREA_FALLBACK, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">5</span></span><span>)
    prompt.click(); prompt.send_keys(text); prompt.send_keys(Keys.ENTER)
    time.sleep(CFG.post_submit_sleep)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 有的站点需要点击按钮</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        btns = drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.SEND_BUTTON)
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> btns:
            btns[</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>].click()
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> Exception:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span></span><span>

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">wait_for_latest_answer</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, timeout</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 等到至少出现一条助手回复</span></span><span>
    wait_for(drv, SELECTORS.ASSISTANT_MESSAGE, timeout)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 关键：等待“生成完成”，按钮从 stop 变回 send</span></span><span>
    wait_until_idle(drv, timeout=CFG.idle_timeout)
    time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.6</span></span><span>)  </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 给 Markdown 渲染一点缓冲</span></span><span>
    nodes = drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.ASSISTANT_MESSAGE)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> nodes[-</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>].text.strip() </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> nodes </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">append_to_md</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">md_file, rel_img, answer, idx</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">with</span></span><span> md_file.</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">open</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"a"</span></span><span>, encoding=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"utf-8"</span></span><span>) </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">as</span></span><span> f:
        f.write(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"\n\n---\n\n## 第 <span class="hljs-subst">{idx}</span></span></span><span> 页\n\n")
        f.write(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"![第 <span class="hljs-subst">{idx}</span></span></span><span> 页](</span><span><span class="hljs-subst">{rel_img.as_posix()}</span></span><span>)\n\n")
        f.write(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"**提问：** <span class="hljs-subst">{CFG.prompt_text}</span></span></span><span>\n\n**回答：**\n\n</span><span><span class="hljs-subst">{answer}</span></span><span>\n")

</span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ===================== MAIN =====================</span></span><span>
</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">main</span></span><span>():
    img_dir, asset_dir = ensure_out_dirs(CFG.out_dir)
    notes_md = CFG.out_dir / </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"notes.md"</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">not</span></span><span> CFG.input_pdf.exists():
        </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"[ERROR] PDF 不存在：<span class="hljs-subst">{CFG.input_pdf}</span></span></span><span>"); sys.exit(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">2</span></span><span>)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"[1/5] PDF → 图片"</span></span><span>)
    pages = pdf_to_images(CFG.input_pdf, img_dir, CFG.render_dpi)
    drv = start_browser(CFG.headless)
    go_to_chat(drv)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"[2/5] 登录成功，开始循环上传..."</span></span><span>)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span></span><span> idx, img_path </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">in</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">enumerate</span></span><span>(pages, start=</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>):
        </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"  - 处理第 <span class="hljs-subst">{idx}</span></span></span><span> 页：</span><span><span class="hljs-subst">{img_path.name}</span></span><span>")
        target = asset_dir / img_path.name
        shutil.copy(img_path, target)
        rel = Path(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"notes_assets"</span></span><span>) / img_path.name

        upload_image(drv, target)                 </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 只允许一张缩略图</span></span><span>
        type_prompt_and_send(drv, CFG.prompt_text)
        answer = wait_for_latest_answer(drv, CFG.answer_timeout)  </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 等到停止→发送</span></span><span>
        append_to_md(notes_md, rel, answer, idx)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"[✔] 完成！结果保存在：<span class="hljs-subst">{notes_md.resolve()}</span></span></span><span>")
    drv.quit()

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> __name__ == </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"__main__"</span></span><span>:
    main()
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-start="9009" data-end="9015">说明</h3>
<ul data-start="9016" data-end="9248">
<li data-start="9016" data-end="9097">
<p data-start="9018" data-end="9097"><code data-start="9018" data-end="9037">wait_until_idle()</code> 会在<strong data-start="9040" data-end="9048">停止按钮</strong>可见时持续等待；一旦它消失，并检测到<strong data-start="9066" data-end="9074">发送按钮</strong>出现，才认为“生成完成”，允许进入下一轮上传。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="9098" data-end="9248">
<p data-start="9100" data-end="9123">为避免 UI 细微差异，我把选择器同时兼容了：</p>
<ul data-start="9126" data-end="9248">
<li data-start="9126" data-end="9197">
<p data-start="9128" data-end="9197"><code data-start="9128" data-end="9155">data-testid="stop-button"</code> / <code data-start="9158" data-end="9174">aria-label*=停止</code> / <code data-start="9177" data-end="9195">aria-label*=Stop</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="9200" data-end="9248">
<p data-start="9202" data-end="9248"><code data-start="9202" data-end="9229">data-testid="send-button"</code> / <code data-start="9232" data-end="9248">aria-label*=发送</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="9250" data-end="9373" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">如果你的页面文案是英文，可以把选择器里“停止/发送”替换或补充 <code data-start="9282" data-end="9327">"aria-label*='Stop'" / "aria-label*='Send'"</code>。<br data-start="9328" data-end="9331">
如果还遇到边角情况，发我一张那段按钮的完整 HTML 节点，我再把选择器对得更精准。</p></div></div></div></div><div class="flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="复制" aria-pressed="false" <pre class="overflow-visible!" data-start="231" data-end="1545"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center 5.25395 18.1657 4.80371 18.1289C4.40306 18.0962 4.04235 18.031 3.70606 17.8867L3.56348 17.8203C3.04244 17.5548 2.60585 17.151 2.30176 16.6553L2.17969 16.4365C1.98788 16.0599 1.90851 15.6541 1.87109 15.1963C1.83431 14.746 1.83496 14.1891 1.83496 13.5V10.667C1.83496 9.978 1.83432 9.42091 1.87109 8.9707C1.90851 8.5127 1.98772 8.10625 2.17969 7.72949L2.30176 7.51172C2.60586 7.0159 3.04236 6.6122 3.56348 6.34668L3.70606 6.28027C4.04237 6.136 4.40303 6.07083 4.80371 6.03809C5.14051 6.01057 5.53708 6.00551 6.00391 6.00391C6.00551 5.53708 6.01057 5.14051 6.03809 4.80371C6.0755 4.34588 6.15483 3.94012 6.34668 3.56348L6.46875 3.34473C6.77282 2.84912 7.20856 2.44514 7.72949 2.17969L7.87207 2.11328C8.20855 1.96886 8.56979 1.90385 8.9707 1.87109C9.42091 1.83432 9.978 1.83496 10.667 1.83496H13.5C14.1891 1.83496 14.746 1.83431 15.1963 1.87109C15.6541 1.90851 16.0599 1.98788 16.4365 2.17969L16.6553 2.30176C17.151 2.60585 17.5548 3.04244 17.8203 3.56348L17.8867 3.70606C18.031 4.04235 18.0962 4.40306 18.1289 4.80371C18.1657 5.25395 18.165 5.81091 18.165 6.5V9.33301Z"></path></svg>复制代码</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">wait_until_idle</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, timeout: <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">25</span></span><span>):
    <span class="hljs-string">"""
    更稳健：优先检测 stop 按钮；若不存在且输入框可用，就认为空闲。
    8s 后仍在生成则尝试点击“停止”强制结束。
    最长等待 25s（可调 CFG.idle_timeout）。
    """</span>
    t0 = time.time()
    force_stop_after = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">8</span></span><span>   </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 8 秒还在生成就点停止</span></span><span>
    last_state = </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">None</span></span><span>

    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span></span><span> time.time() - t0 &lt; timeout:
        has_stop = </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">len</span></span><span>(drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.STOP_BUTTON)) &gt; </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>
        has_send = </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">len</span></span><span>(drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.SEND_BUTTON)) &gt; </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>
        prompt_ready = </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">len</span></span><span>(drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.PROMPT_AREA)) &gt; </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">or</span></span><span> \
                       </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">len</span></span><span>(drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.PROMPT_AREA_FALLBACK)) &gt; </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>

        state = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"stop=<span class="hljs-subst">{has_stop}</span></span></span><span>, send=</span><span><span class="hljs-subst">{has_send}</span></span><span>, prompt=</span><span><span class="hljs-subst">{prompt_ready}</span></span><span>"
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> state != last_state:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"[idle] <span class="hljs-subst">{state}</span></span></span><span>")
            last_state = state

        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> has_stop:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 生成中：超过阈值就点“停止”</span></span><span>
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> time.time() - t0 &gt; force_stop_after:
                </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
                    drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.STOP_BUTTON)[</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>].click()
                    </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"[idle] 点击 停止"</span></span><span>)
                </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> Exception:
                    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span></span><span>
            time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.3</span></span><span>)
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">continue</span></span><span>

        </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 没有 stop：如果有 send 按钮，或输入框可用（可视作空闲）</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> has_send </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">or</span></span><span> prompt_ready:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span>

        time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.3</span></span><span>)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">raise</span></span><span> TimeoutException(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"等待模型空闲超时（未检测到 stop/send，或输入框不可用）。"</span></span><span>)
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1547" data-end="1550">
<h3 data-start="1552" data-end="1576">2) 替换 <code data-start="1562" data-end="1576">upload_image</code></h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible!" data-start="1577" data-end="2214"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">upload_image</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, img_path: Path</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 在上传前确认空闲；但不因检测失败而卡死（最多等 CFG.idle_timeout）</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        wait_until_idle(drv, timeout=</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">min</span></span><span>(CFG.idle_timeout, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">25</span></span><span>))
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> TimeoutException:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"[upload] 未确认到空闲，但继续尝试上传（容错）"</span></span><span>)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 彻底清理旧图片 DOM</span></span><span>
    clear_all_uploads(drv)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 执行上传</span></span><span>
    file_input = wait_for(drv, SELECTORS.FILE_INPUT, CFG.upload_timeout)
    drv.execute_script(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"arguments[0].style='';"</span></span><span>, file_input)
    file_input.send_keys(</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span>(img_path.resolve()))
    </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"[upload] 发送文件：<span class="hljs-subst">{img_path.name}</span></span></span><span>")

    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 等到预览==1 且稳定</span></span><span>
    wait_stable_tile_count(drv, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>, CFG.upload_timeout)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"[upload] 预览稳定为 1"</span></span><span>)
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="2216" data-end="2219">
<h3 data-start="2221" data-end="2239">还可以顺手调两处配置（可选）</h3>
<ul data-start="2240" data-end="2289">
<li data-start="2240" data-end="2276">
<p data-start="2242" data-end="2276">把 <code data-start="2244" data-end="2262">CFG.idle_timeout</code> 先设小点，比如 <code data-start="2271" data-end="2275">30</code>；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2277" data-end="2289">
<p data-start="2279" data-end="2289">首次跑通再逐步调大。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2291" data-end="2294">
<h3 data-start="2296" data-end="2307">为什么这么改？</h3>
<ul data-start="2308" data-end="2444">
<li data-start="2308" data-end="2372">
<p data-start="2310" data-end="2372">有些皮肤/语言下，“发送/停止”按钮的 <code data-start="2330" data-end="2343">data-testid</code>/<code data-start="2344" data-end="2356">aria-label</code> 可能不一致，仅靠它会误等。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2373" data-end="2411">
<p data-start="2375" data-end="2411">新逻辑：<strong data-start="2379" data-end="2398">没有 stop 且输入框可编辑</strong> ⇒ 可以上传下一张。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2412" data-end="2444">
<p data-start="2414" data-end="2444">如果确实在“生成中”很久，主动点击“停止”，保证流程继续走。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2446" data-end="2449">
<p data-start="2451" data-end="2550" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">直接替换这两段再跑一次。如果还有卡住，控制台会打印 <code data-start="2477" data-end="2516">[idle] stop=..., send=..., prompt=...</code>，把那几行状态贴给我，我就按照你的真实 DOM 再把选择器对得更窄。</p></div></div></div></div><div class="flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[72rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn" tabindex="-1"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="ed1d9577-62fe-41ae-a702-da9ebe177559" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-thinking"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="114">你看到它“老是点停止”，是因为我在上一版里为了防卡死，写了个<strong data-start="30" data-end="47">8 秒还在生成就自动点停止</strong>的逻辑。你要<strong data-start="53" data-end="65">完整等待模型输出</strong>，就需要把这个“强制停止”去掉，仅仅<strong data-start="83" data-end="111">等待 stop 按钮消失 / send 按钮出现</strong>即可。</p>
<p data-start="116" data-end="140">下面给你两处<strong data-start="122" data-end="130">替换代码</strong>（只改这两段就行）：</p>
<hr data-start="142" data-end="145">
<h2 data-start="147" data-end="185">1) 用这个替换 <code data-start="159" data-end="176">wait_until_idle</code>（不再自动点停止）</h2>

10.9209 7.36328C10.5374 7.33197 10.0439 7.33203 9.33301 7.33203H6.5C5.78896 7.33203 5.29563 7.33195 4.91211 7.36328C4.63016 7.38632 4.44065 7.42413 4.29688 7.47559L4.16699 7.53125C3.86488 7.68518 3.61186 7.9196 3.43555 8.20703L3.36524 8.33399C3.28478 8.49198 3.22795 8.70352 3.19727 9.0791C3.16595 9.46259 3.16504 9.95611 3.16504 10.667V13.5C3.16504 14.211 3.16593 14.7044 3.19727 15.0879C3.22797 3.94012 6.34668 3.56348L6.46875 3.34473C6.77282 2.84912 7.20856 2.44514 7.72949 2.17969L7.87207 2.11328C8.20855 1.96886 8.56979 1.90385 8.9707 1.87109C9.42091 1.83432 9.978 1.83496 10.667 1.83496H13.5C14.1891 1.83496 14.746 1.83431 15.1963 1.87109C15.6541 1.90851 16.0599 1.98788 16.4365 2.17969L16.6553 2.30176C17.151 2.60585 17.5548 3.04244 17.8203 3.56348L17.8867 3.70606C18.031 4.04235 18.0962 4.40306 18.1289 4.80371C18.1657 5.25395 18.165 5.81091 18.165 6.5V9.33301Z"></path></svg>复制代码</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">wait_until_idle</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, timeout: <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">None</span></span><span>):
    <span class="hljs-string">"""
    仅等待：stop 按钮消失 且 发送可用（或输入框可用），绝不点击“停止”。
    """</span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> timeout </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">is</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">None</span></span><span>:
        timeout = CFG.idle_timeout  </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 可在配置里调大/调小</span></span><span>

    t0 = time.time()
    last_state = </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">None</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 更鲁棒的“发送可用”判断：要么出现 send-button，要么 composer 的输入框可编辑</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span></span><span> time.time() - t0 &lt; timeout:
        has_stop = </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">len</span></span><span>(drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.STOP_BUTTON)) &gt; </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>
        has_send = </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">len</span></span><span>(drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.SEND_BUTTON)) &gt; </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>
        prompt_ready = </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">len</span></span><span>(drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.PROMPT_AREA)) &gt; </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">or</span></span><span> \
                       </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">len</span></span><span>(drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.PROMPT_AREA_FALLBACK)) &gt; </span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>

        state = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"stop=<span class="hljs-subst">{has_stop}</span></span></span><span>, send=</span><span><span class="hljs-subst">{has_send}</span></span><span>, prompt=</span><span><span class="hljs-subst">{prompt_ready}</span></span><span>"
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> state != last_state:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"[idle] <span class="hljs-subst">{state}</span></span></span><span>")
            last_state = state

        </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 生成中 → 等</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> has_stop:
            time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.35</span></span><span>)
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">continue</span></span><span>

        </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 不在生成：出现 send 或输入框可编辑，即视为空闲</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> has_send </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">or</span></span><span> prompt_ready:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span>

        time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.35</span></span><span>)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">raise</span></span><span> TimeoutException(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"等待模型生成完成超时（stop 未消失或发送不可用）。"</span></span><span>)
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>

<h2 data-start="1271" data-end="1308">2) 用这个替换 <code data-start="1283" data-end="1297">upload_image</code>（仍然在空闲后才上传）</h2>
<pre class="overflow-visible!" data-start="1310" data-end="1866"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="复制"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-sm"><path d="M12.668 10.667C12.668 3.94012 6.34668 3.56348L6.46875 3.34473C6.77282 2.84912 7.20856 2.44514 7.72949 2.17969L7.87207 2.11328C8.20855 1.96886 8.56979 1.90385 8.9707 1.87109C9.42091 1.83432 9.978 1.83496 10.667 1.83496H13.5C14.1891 1.83496 14.746 1.83431 15.1963 1.87109C15.6541 1.90851 16.0599 1.98788 16.4365 2.17969L16.6553 2.30176C17.151 2.60585 17.5548 3.04244 17.8203 3.56348L17.8867 3.70606C18.031 4.04235 18.0962 4.40306 18.1289 4.80371C18.1657 5.25395 18.165 5.81091 18.165 6.5V9.33301Z"></path></svg>复制代码</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">upload_image</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, img_path: Path</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 上传前先确认空闲（不点击停止）</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        wait_until_idle(drv)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> TimeoutException:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"[upload] 警告：未能确认空闲，仍尝试上传（可能站点选择器需再对齐）"</span></span><span>)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 彻底清理历史预览，再上传</span></span><span>
    clear_all_uploads(drv)
    file_input = wait_for(drv, SELECTORS.FILE_INPUT, CFG.upload_timeout)
    drv.execute_script(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"arguments[0].style='';"</span></span><span>, file_input)
    file_input.send_keys(</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span>(img_path.resolve()))
    </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"[upload] 发送文件：<span class="hljs-subst">{img_path.name}</span></span></span><span>")
    wait_stable_tile_count(drv, </span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>, CFG.upload_timeout)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">print</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"[upload] 预览稳定为 1"</span></span><span>)
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1868" data-end="1871">
<h2 data-start="1873" data-end="1891">3)（可选）把等待时间调长一点</h2>
<p data-start="1892" data-end="1898">在配置里把：</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible!" data-start="1899" data-end="1936"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl">python</div><div class="sticky top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="复制"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-sm"><path d="M12.668 10.667C12.668 </span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1937" data-end="1960">按你的网络/模型速度适当加大（比如 240）。</p>
<hr data-start="1962" data-end="1965">
<h3 data-start="1967" data-end="1973">说明</h3>
<ul data-start="1974" data-end="2505">
<li data-start="1974" data-end="2032">
<p data-start="1976" data-end="2032">之前之所以“总点停止”，就是我写了“超过 8 秒还在生成就点停止”的容错分支。你现在要完整输出，就把它删除即可。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2033" data-end="2103">
<p data-start="2035" data-end="2103">这版只<strong data-start="2038" data-end="2048">观察按钮状态</strong>：看到 <code data-start="2052" data-end="2065">stop-button</code> 就等；消失且 <code data-start="2073" data-end="2086">send-button</code>/输入框可用时，才进入下一轮上传。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2104" data-end="2505">
<p data-start="2106" data-end="2149">如果站点的按钮标识和我写的不完全一致（不同语言皮肤），把 <code data-start="2135" data-end="2146">SELECTORS</code> 里：</p>
<ul data-start="2152" data-end="2505">
<li data-start="2152" data-end="2301">
<p data-start="2154" data-end="2301"><code data-start="2154" data-end="2301">STOP_BUTTON = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, "button[data-testid='stop-button'], button#composer-submit-button[aria-label*='停止'], button[aria-label*='Stop']")</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="2304" data-end="2505">
<p data-start="2306" data-end="2505"><code data-start="2306" data-end="2453">SEND_BUTTON = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, "button[data-testid='send-button'], button#composer-submit-button[aria-label*='发送'], button[aria-label*='Send']")</code><br>
根据你页面里实际的 <code data-start="2466" data-end="2479">data-testid</code> / <code data-start="2482" data-end="2494">aria-label</code> 再加一两个候选即可。</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2507" data-end="2524">改完这两处再跑，控制台会打印类似：</p>

<h2 data-start="294" data-end="319">1) 新增/替换选择器（如果你还没有就补上）</h2>

class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title class_">SELECTORS</span></span><span>:
    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ……（你现有的保持不变）</span></span><span>
    ASSISTANT_TURN = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"[data-message-author-role='assistant'], article[data-message-author-role='assistant']"</span></span><span>)
    COPY_BUTTON_IN_TURN = (By.CSS_SELECTOR,
        </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"button[data-testid='copy-turn-action-button'], "</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"button[aria-label*='复制'], button[aria-label*='拷贝'], "</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"button[aria-label*='Copy']"</span></span><span>)
    OVERFLOW_BUTTON_IN_TURN = (By.CSS_SELECTOR,
        </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"button[data-testid='overflow-menu-trigger'], "</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"button[aria-label*='更多'], button[aria-label*='More']"</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 菜单项：复制为 Markdown</span></span><span>
    MENU_COPY_AS_MD = (By.XPATH,
        </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"//div[@role='menu']//div[contains(., '复制为 Markdown') or contains(., 'Copy as Markdown')]"</span></span><span>)
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
