4.04235 18.0962 4.40306 18.1289 4.80371C18.1657 5.25395 18.165 5.81091 18.165 6.5V9.33301Z"></path></svg>复制代码</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">get_last_assistant_turn</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"""定位最后一条助手消息（整块 turn 区域，用于在其中找【复制】按钮）"""</span></span><span>
    turns = drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.ASSISTANT_TURN)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">not</span></span><span> turns:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">raise</span></span><span> TimeoutException(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"未找到助手消息 turn。"</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> turns[-</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>]

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">copy_markdown_from_last_turn</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, wait_secs: <span class="hljs-built_in">float</span></span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">5.0</span></span><span>) -&gt; </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span>:
    <span class="hljs-string">"""
    点击最后一条助手消息里的【复制/Copy】或菜单中的【复制为 Markdown】，
    然后用 pyperclip 从系统剪贴板读取 Markdown。
    """</span>
    turn = get_last_assistant_turn(drv)
    drv.execute_script(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"arguments[0].scrollIntoView({block:'center'});"</span></span><span>, turn)
    time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.2</span></span><span>)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 1) 直接找“复制”按钮</span></span><span>
    btns = turn.find_elements(*SELECTORS.COPY_BUTTON_IN_TURN)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> btns:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
            btns[</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>].click()
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> Exception:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span></span><span>:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 2) 有些界面“复制为 Markdown”在“更多”菜单里</span></span><span>
        more = turn.find_elements(*SELECTORS.OVERFLOW_BUTTON_IN_TURN)
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> more:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
                more[</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>].click()
                time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.2</span></span><span>)
                items = drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.MENU_COPY_AS_MD)
                </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> items:
                    items[</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>].click()
                </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span></span><span>:
                    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 如果没有“复制为 Markdown”，退而求其次：菜单里第一个“复制”</span></span><span>
                    alt = drv.find_elements(By.XPATH, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"//div[@role='menu']//div[contains(., '复制') or contains(., 'Copy')]"</span></span><span>)
                    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> alt:
                        alt[</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>].click()
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> Exception:
                </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span></span><span>

    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 3) 从系统剪贴板读 Markdown</span></span><span>
    start = time.time()
    md = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span></span><span> time.time() - start &lt; wait_secs:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
            md = pyperclip.paste() </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">or</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> Exception:
            md = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> md.strip():
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">break</span></span><span>
        time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.2</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> md
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="2746" data-end="2749">
<h2 data-start="2751" data-end="2773">3) 修改“等待回答并获取内容”的逻辑</h2>
<p data-start="2775" data-end="2821">把你原来的 <code data-start="2781" data-end="2810">wait_for_latest_answer(...)</code> <strong data-start="2811" data-end="2820">整段替换为</strong>：</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible!" data-start="2823" data-end="3467"><div class="contain-inline-size rounded-2xl relative bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary"><div class="flex items-center text-token-text-secondary px-4 py-2 text-xs font-sans justify-between h-9 bg-token-sidebar-surface-primary select-none rounded-t-2xl">python</div><div class="sticky top-9"><div class="absolute end-0 bottom-0 flex h-9 items-center pe-2"><div class="bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary text-token-text-secondary flex items-center gap-4 rounded-sm px-2 font-sans text-xs"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-1" aria-label="复制"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon-sm"><path d="M12.668 10.667C12.668 9.95614 12.668 9.46258 12.6367 9.0791C12.6137 8.79732 12.5758 8.60761 12.5244 8.46387L12.4688 8.33399C12.3148 8.03193 12.0803 7.77885 11.793 7.60254L11.666 7.53125C11.508 7.45087 11.2963 7.39395 3.61186 7.9196 3.43555 8.20703L3.36524 8.33399C3.28478 8.49198 3.22795 8.70352 3.19727 9.0791C3.16595 9.46259 3.16504 9.95611 3.16504 10.667V13.5C3.16504 14.211 3.16593 14.7044 3.19727 15.0879C3.22797 16.835H9.33301C10.0439 16.835 10.5374 16.8341 10.9209 16.8027C11.2965 16.772 11.508 16.7152 11.666 16.6348L11.793 16.5645C12.0804 16.3881 12.3148 16.1351 12.4688 15.833L12.5244 15.7031C12.5759 15.5594 4.04235 18.0962 4.40306 18.1289 4.80371C18.1657 5.25395 18.165 5.81091 18.165 6.5V9.33301Z"></path></svg>复制代码</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">wait_for_latest_answer</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, timeout</span></span><span>):
    <span class="hljs-string">"""
    等待出现助手回复 → 等待生成彻底完成（stop→send 或输入可用）
    → 点击复制按钮拿到 Markdown；如果复制失败，回退到取纯文本。
    """</span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 先等“出现一条助手消息”</span></span><span>
    wait_for(drv, SELECTORS.ASSISTANT_TURN, timeout)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 等生成彻底完成（你脚里已有 wait_until_idle）</span></span><span>
    wait_until_idle(drv)
    time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.4</span></span><span>)  </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 渲染缓冲</span></span><span>

    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 复制为 Markdown</span></span><span>
    md = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        md = copy_markdown_from_last_turn(drv, wait_secs=</span><span><span class="hljs-number">5.0</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> Exception:
        md = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>

    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> md.strip():
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> md  </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ✅ 返回 Markdown</span></span><span>

    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 兜底：如果复制失败，退回纯文本</span></span><span>
    nodes = drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.ASSISTANT_MESSAGE)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> nodes[-</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>].text.strip() </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> nodes </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="3469" data-end="3472">
<h2 data-start="3474" data-end="3498">4) 在落盘时保持 Markdown 原样</h2>
<p data-start="3500" data-end="3559"><code data-start="3500" data-end="3519">append_to_md(...)</code> 里，写回答部分用<strong data-start="3528" data-end="3534">原样</strong>写入，不要再做额外格式化（保留 <code data-start="3550" data-end="3554">md</code>）。比如：</p>

class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">append_to_md</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">md_file: Path, rel_img: Path, answer_md: <span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span></span><span>, idx: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">int</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">with</span></span><span> md_file.</span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">open</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"a"</span></span><span>, encoding=</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"utf-8"</span></span><span>) </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">as</span></span><span> f:
        f.write(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"\n\n---\n\n## 第 <span class="hljs-subst">{idx}</span></span></span><span> 页\n\n")
        f.write(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"![第 <span class="hljs-subst">{idx}</span></span></span><span> 页](</span><span><span class="hljs-subst">{rel_img.as_posix()}</span></span><span>)\n\n")
        f.write(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"**提问：** <span class="hljs-subst">{CFG.prompt_text}</span></span></span><span>\n\n")
        f.write(answer_md)  </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 直接写入 Markdown（不加额外包裹）</span></span><span>
        f.write(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"\n"</span></span><span>)
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="3932" data-end="3935">
<h2 data-start="3937" data-end="3947">5) 运行效果</h2>
<ul data-start="3949" data-end="4122">
<li data-start="3949" data-end="4042">
<p data-start="3951" data-end="4042">每页：上传 1 张图 → 发送固定提示词 → <strong data-start="3974" data-end="3982">等生成完</strong> → 点击“复制/复制为 Markdown” → 从剪贴板读 MD → 追加到 <code data-start="4022" data-end="4039">output/notes.md</code>。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="4043" data-end="4122">
<p data-start="4045" data-end="4122">如果“复制按钮/菜单”在你的皮肤里叫法不同，只需把上面选择器里的 <code data-start="4078" data-end="4105">aria-label*='复制' / 'Copy'</code> 这类匹配再补充一两个关键词即可。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="4124" data-end="4127">
<p data-start="4129" data-end="4211" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">如果你愿意，发我一小段“复制按钮”所在那行的完整 HTML（<code data-start="4159" data-end="4187">button ... aria-label="？？"</code>），我可以把选择器精确到你页面的文案，这样更稳。</p></div></div></div></div><div class="flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center <p data-start="217" data-end="225">根因通常有两个：</p>
<ol data-start="226" data-end="301">
<li data-start="226" data-end="273">
<p data-start="229" data-end="273">没真的点到“复制 / 复制为 Markdown”按钮（或点了但被遮挡/菜单未展开）；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="274" data-end="301">
<p data-start="277" data-end="301">复制成功与否没有验证，直接读了<strong data-start="292" data-end="300">旧剪贴板</strong>。</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="303" data-end="325">下面给你一组<strong data-start="309" data-end="316">小补丁</strong>，让复制逻辑更稳：</p>
<hr data-start="327" data-end="330">
<h2 data-start="332" data-end="343">改法（最小改动）</h2>
<h3 data-start="345" data-end="382">A. 复制前先放哨兵值，再点击复制，并等待剪贴板“变化 + 非空”</h3>
<p data-start="383" data-end="488">把你脚本里的 <code data-start="390" data-end="420">copy_markdown_from_last_turn</code> 换成这一版（确保已 <code data-start="431" data-end="449">import pyperclip</code>）。<span 4.04235 18.0962 4.40306 18.1289 4.80371C18.1657 5.25395 18.165 5.81091 18.165 6.5V9.33301Z"></path></svg>复制代码</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">copy_markdown_from_last_turn</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, wait_secs: <span class="hljs-built_in">float</span></span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">8.0</span></span><span>) -&gt; </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span>:
    <span class="hljs-string">"""
    复制最后一条助手消息为 Markdown：
    1) 先把剪贴板写入哨兵值，防止读到旧内容；
    2) 优先点击“复制为 Markdown”（菜单项），其次是“复制”按钮；
    3) 等待剪贴板变化与非空；若失败返回空串。
    """</span>
    SENTINEL = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"__WAITING_FOR_MD__"</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        pyperclip.copy(SENTINEL)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> Exception:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span></span><span>

    turn = get_last_assistant_turn(drv)
    drv.execute_script(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"arguments[0].scrollIntoView({block:'center'});"</span></span><span>, turn)
    time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.2</span></span><span>)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 优先走“更多 → 复制为 Markdown”</span></span><span>
    used_action = </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">False</span></span><span>
    more = turn.find_elements(*SELECTORS.OVERFLOW_BUTTON_IN_TURN)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> more:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
            more[</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>].click()
            time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.25</span></span><span>)
            items = drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.MENU_COPY_AS_MD)
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> items:
                items[</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>].click()
                used_action = </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span></span><span>:
                </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 菜单里没有“复制为 Markdown”，尝试菜单中的“复制”</span></span><span>
                alt = drv.find_elements(By.XPATH, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"//div[@role='menu']//div[contains(., '复制') or contains(., 'Copy')]"</span></span><span>)
                </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> alt:
                    alt[</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>].click()
                    used_action = </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> Exception:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span></span><span>

    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 如果没用到菜单，再尝试直接“复制”按钮</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">not</span></span><span> used_action:
        btns = turn.find_elements(*SELECTORS.COPY_BUTTON_IN_TURN)
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> btns:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
                btns[</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>].click()
                used_action = </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> Exception:
                </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span></span><span>

    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 等剪贴板变化</span></span><span>
    start = time.time()
    md = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span></span><span> time.time() - start &lt; wait_secs:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
            md = pyperclip.paste() </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">or</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> Exception:
            md = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> md </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">and</span></span><span> md != SENTINEL:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">break</span></span><span>
        time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.2</span></span><span>)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> md.strip()
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-start="2214" data-end="2243">B. 复制失败就回退纯文本，但在 md 里做个标识</h3>

class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span>    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> md:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> md  </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ✅ 返回 Markdown</span></span><span>

    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 兜底：复制失败 → 退回纯文本并加上提示</span></span><span>
    nodes = drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.ASSISTANT_MESSAGE)
    fallback = nodes[-</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>].text.strip() </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> nodes </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"&gt; ⚠️ 未能复制为 Markdown，以下为纯文本回退：\n\n<span class="hljs-subst">{fallback}</span></span></span><span>"
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-start="2595" data-end="2634">C.（可选）检测“已复制”气泡/Toast 再读剪贴板（若你的界面有）</h3>

class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">wait_copied_toast</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, secs=<span class="hljs-number">2.0</span></span></span><span>):
    end = time.time() + secs
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span></span><span> time.time() &lt; end:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 你可以根据实际 DOM 调整选择器，比如 role='status' 的内容包含“复制”</span></span><span>
        toasts = drv.find_elements(By.XPATH, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"//*[contains(., '已复制') or contains(., 'Copied')]"</span></span><span>)
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> toasts:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>
        time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.1</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">False</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="3020" data-end="3062">然后在点击复制后 <code data-start="3029" data-end="3053">wait_copied_toast(drv)</code> 一下再读剪贴板。</p>

</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="3230" data-end="3248">正常应返回 <code data-start="3236" data-end="3245">"hello"</code>。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3249" data-end="3454">
<p data-start="3251" data-end="3454"><strong data-start="3251" data-end="3263">按钮选择器对不上</strong>：你给的截图里按钮在消息卡片右上角工具条里，通常有 <code data-start="3289" data-end="3328">data-testid="copy-turn-action-button"</code>；我在选择器里已经兼容了 <code data-start="3341" data-end="3380">data-testid / aria-label*='复制'/'Copy'</code>，如果你的文案不同，把 <code data-start="3392" data-end="3423">SELECTORS.COPY_BUTTON_IN_TURN</code> 里加上那串实际的 <code data-start="3433" data-end="3445">aria-label</code> 关键字即可。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3455" data-end="3559">
<p data-start="3457" data-end="3559"><strong data-start="3457" data-end="3478">复制为 Markdown 在菜单里</strong>：如果“更多”按钮的选择器不同，同理把 <code data-start="3498" data-end="3523">OVERFLOW_BUTTON_IN_TURN</code> 补上实际的 <code data-start="3530" data-end="3543">data-testid</code> 或 <code data-start="3546" data-end="3558">aria-label</code>。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="3561" data-end="3564">
<h2 data-start="3566" data-end="3589">为什么你现在的 md 里会出现函数源码？</h2>
<p data-start="3590" data-end="3746">从你上传的 <code data-start="3596" data-end="3606">notes.md</code> 能看出插入的是 <code data-start="3615" data-end="3629">append_to_md</code> 这段函数定义，说明当时剪贴板里正好是这段代码——复制动作没成功，脚本直接把<strong data-start="3667" data-end="3675">旧剪贴板</strong>写进去了。按上面“哨兵值 + 等变化”的方法，就不会再发生这种误写。<span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="relative inline-flex items-center"><button class="ms-1 flex h-[22px] items-center rounded-xl px-2 relative bottom-[-2px] bg-[#f4f4f4] text-token-text-secondary! hover:bg-token-bg-secondary dark:bg-token-main-surface-secondary dark:hover:bg-token-bg-secondary"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" alt="文件" class="h-[16px] w-[16px] object-contain"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M11.2598 2.25191C11.8396 2.25191 12.2381 2.24808 12.6201 2.33981L12.8594 2.40719C13.0957 2.48399 13.3228 2.5886 13.5352 (module) pyperclip
Pyperclip

A cross-platform clipboard module for Python, with copy &amp; paste functions for plain text. By Al Sweigart al@inventwithpython.com BSD License

Usage:

import pyperclip
pyperclip.copy('The text to be copied to the clipboard.')
spam = pyperclip.paste()
if not pyperclip.is_available():

print("Copy functionality unavailable!")

On Windows, no additional modules are needed. On Mac, the pyobjc module is used, falling back to the pbcopy and pbpaste cli commands. (These commands should come with OS X.). On Linux, install xclip, xsel, or wl-clipboard (for "wayland" sessions) via package manager. For example, in Debian: sudo apt-get install xclip sudo apt-get install xsel sudo apt-get install wl-clipboard

Otherwise on Linux, you will need the qtpy or PyQt5 modules installed.

This module does not work with PyGObject yet.

Cygwin is currently not supported.

Security Note: This module runs programs with these names:

which
pbcopy
pbpaste
xclip
xsel
wl-copy/wl-paste
klipper
qdbus
A malicious user could rename or add programs with these names, tricking

Pyperclip into running them with whatever permissions the Python process has. 什么意思</div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-end"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex </span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="394" data-end="422">我们脚本里用它从系统剪贴板读出 Markdown 文本。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="424" data-end="527">
<p data-start="427" data-end="436"><strong data-start="427" data-end="436">提示的含义</strong></p>
<ul data-start="440" data-end="527">
<li data-start="440" data-end="483">
<p data-start="442" data-end="483">Pylance（VSCode 的 Python 语言服务器）找不到这个库的源文件；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="487" data-end="509">
<p data-start="489" data-end="509">但如果你用命令行装了，它是能正常运行的；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="513" data-end="527">
<p data-start="515" data-end="527">如果没装，则需要自己装。</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="529" data-end="532">

</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="797" data-end="814">看到输出 <code data-start="802" data-end="806">OK</code> 就说明能用了。</p>
<h4 data-start="816" data-end="839">方法二：VS Code 还提示红线？</h4>
<ul data-start="840" data-end="969">
<li data-start="840" data-end="870">
<p data-start="842" data-end="870">打开 VSCode 命令面板（Ctrl+Shift+P）</p>
</li>
<li data-start="871" data-end="904">
<p data-start="873" data-end="904">搜索：<code data-start="876" data-end="904">Python: Select Interpreter</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="905" data-end="949">
<p data-start="907" data-end="949">选中与你运行脚本相同的环境（通常带 <code data-start="925" data-end="933">(base)</code> 或 <code data-start="936" data-end="943">conda</code> 的那一行）</p>
</li>
<li data-start="950" data-end="969">
<p data-start="952" data-end="969">重启 VSCode，红线就会消失。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="971" data-end="974">

<p data-start="1122" data-end="1138">Windows 不需要额外配置。</p>
<hr data-start="1140" data-end="1143">
<h3 data-start="1145" data-end="1153">✅ 结论</h3>
<p data-start="1154" data-end="1236">这不是脚本出错，只是 VSCode 检测不到模块。<br data-start="1179" data-end="1182">
<strong data-start="1182" data-end="1236">只要运行 <code data-start="1189" data-end="1212">pip install pyperclip</code> 成功，脚本就能正常复制 Markdown。</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1238" data-end="1241">
<p data-start="1243" data-end="1325" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">要不要我帮你加一个自动检测 pyperclip 是否可用的保护逻辑？<br data-start="1277" data-end="1280">
比如自动提示“未检测到剪贴板模块，请手动复制 Markdown”。这样即使没装好也不会卡。</p></div></div></div></div><div class="flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="复制" aria-pressed="false" light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="73">太有用了！“点复制后变成 ✔️，几秒再变回去”给了我们一个很好用的<strong data-start="33" data-end="41">完成信号</strong>。<br data-start="42" data-end="45">
我把复制逻辑再加固三件事，同时保留“剪贴板哨兵值”那套：</p>
<ol data-start="75" data-end="280">
<li data-start="75" data-end="127">
<p data-start="78" data-end="127"><strong data-start="78" data-end="100">优先点击消息卡片右上角的「复制」按钮</strong>（你截图里 <code data-start="106" data-end="123">aria-label="复制"</code>）。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="128" data-end="248">
<p data-start="131" data-end="137">点击后：</p>
<ul data-start="141" data-end="248">
<li data-start="141" data-end="204">
<p data-start="143" data-end="204">等待<strong data-start="145" data-end="161">按钮的图标/文案发生变化</strong>（<code data-start="162" data-end="174">aria-label</code> 变成“已复制/Copied”，或 SVG 发生变化）；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="208" data-end="248">
<p data-start="210" data-end="248">同时用 <strong data-start="214" data-end="230">pyperclip 哨兵</strong>检测<strong data-start="232" data-end="245">剪贴板内容真的更新</strong>。</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start="249" data-end="280">
<p data-start="252" data-end="280">两个条件只要任意一个满足就读取剪贴板；否则兜底到纯文本。</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="282" data-end="322">把下面这三段粘到你的脚本里，<strong data-start="296" data-end="314">替换同名函数 / 选择器即可</strong>（其他不用动）。</p>
<hr data-start="324" data-end="327">

ASSISTANT_TURN = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"[data-message-author-role='assistant'], article[data-message-author-role='assistant']"</span></span><span>)
COPY_BUTTON_IN_TURN = (By.CSS_SELECTOR,
    </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"button[data-testid='copy-turn-action-button'], "</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"button[aria-label*='复制'], button[aria-label*='拷贝'], "</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"button[aria-label*='Copy']"</span></span><span>)
</span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 按钮变成勾时常会把 aria-label 改成“已复制/Copied”</span></span><span>
COPIED_STATE_MATCHERS = [
    (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"button[aria-label*='已复制']"</span></span><span>),
    (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"button[aria-label*='Copied']"</span></span><span>),

<h3 data-start="879" data-end="910">2) 点击复制 + 观察“勾 ✔”反馈 + 剪贴板哨兵</h3>

class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> pyperclip

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">get_last_assistant_turn</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv</span></span><span>):
    turns = drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.ASSISTANT_TURN)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">not</span></span><span> turns:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">raise</span></span><span> TimeoutException(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"未找到助手消息 turn。"</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> turns[-</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>]

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">wait_button_feedback_or_clipboard</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, btn, sentinel: <span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span></span><span>, timeout: </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">float</span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">5.0</span></span><span>) -&gt; </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">bool</span></span><span>:
    </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"""等待两种反馈任一发生：按钮进入“已复制”状态 或 剪贴板不等于哨兵。"""</span></span><span>
    end = time.time() + timeout
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span></span><span> time.time() &lt; end:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 1) aria-label/按钮状态变化（✔）</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span></span><span> how, what </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">in</span></span><span> SELECTORS.COPIED_STATE_MATCHERS:
                </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> get_last_assistant_turn(drv).find_elements(how, what):
                    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> Exception:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 2) 剪贴板变化</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
            text = (pyperclip.paste() </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">or</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>).strip()
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> text </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">and</span></span><span> text != sentinel:
                </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> Exception:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span></span><span>
        time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.15</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">False</span></span><span>

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">copy_markdown_from_last_turn</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, wait_secs: <span class="hljs-built_in">float</span></span></span><span> = </span><span><span class="hljs-number">8.0</span></span><span>) -&gt; </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span>:
    <span class="hljs-string">"""
    点击【复制】或菜单项【复制为 Markdown】，
    以“✔ 反馈”或剪贴板变化作为成功信号，再读取 Markdown。
    """</span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 置哨兵，防止读到旧剪贴板</span></span><span>
    SENTINEL = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"__WAITING_FOR_MD__"</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        pyperclip.copy(SENTINEL)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> Exception:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span></span><span>

    turn = get_last_assistant_turn(drv)
    drv.execute_script(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"arguments[0].scrollIntoView({block:'center'});"</span></span><span>, turn)
    time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.2</span></span><span>)

    used_action = </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">False</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 先点卡片上的“复制”</span></span><span>
    btns = turn.find_elements(*SELECTORS.COPY_BUTTON_IN_TURN)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> btns:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
            btns[</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>].click()
            used_action = </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>
            </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 等“✔或剪贴板变化”</span></span><span>
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">not</span></span><span> wait_button_feedback_or_clipboard(drv, btns[</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0</span></span><span>], SENTINEL, timeout=wait_secs):
                </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 若无反馈，继续尝试菜单</span></span><span>
                used_action = </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">False</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> Exception:
            used_action = </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">False</span></span><span>

    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 菜单里的“复制为 Markdown / Copy as Markdown”</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">not</span></span><span> used_action:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 你若已实现 OVERFLOW_BUTTON_IN_TURN/MENU_COPY_AS_MD，也可以在这里补充菜单逻辑</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span></span><span>

    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 最终读剪贴板</span></span><span>
    md = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        md = (pyperclip.paste() </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">or</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>).strip()
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> md == SENTINEL:
            md = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> Exception:
        md = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> md
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>

<h3 data-start="3021" data-end="3057">3) 获取回答：优先 Markdown，失败回退纯文本（带提示）</h3>

class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">wait_for_latest_answer</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, timeout</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 等至少一条助手消息出现</span></span><span>
    wait_for(drv, SELECTORS.ASSISTANT_TURN, timeout)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 等生成彻底完成（stop→send）</span></span><span>
    wait_until_idle(drv)
    time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.4</span></span><span>)

    md = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        md = copy_markdown_from_last_turn(drv, wait_secs=</span><span><span class="hljs-number">8.0</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> Exception:
        md = </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>

    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> md:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> md  </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># ✅ 原生 Markdown</span></span><span>

    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 兜底：取纯文本并打标</span></span><span>
    nodes = drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.ASSISTANT_MESSAGE)
    fallback = nodes[-</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>].text.strip() </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> nodes </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"&gt; ⚠️ 未能复制为 Markdown，以下为纯文本回退：\n\n<span class="hljs-subst">{fallback}</span></span></span><span>"
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="3617" data-end="3620">
<h3 data-start="3622" data-end="3635">为什么这次能稳定？</h3>
<ul data-start="3636" data-end="3796">
<li data-start="3636" data-end="3750">
<p data-start="3638" data-end="3750"><strong data-start="3638" data-end="3646">两路信号</strong>判断复制成功：<br data-start="3653" data-end="3656">
a) 你说的“<strong data-start="3665" data-end="3677">按钮变成对钩 ✔</strong>”——我们用 <code data-start="3684" data-end="3712">aria-label*='已复制'/'Copied'</code> 或者按钮自身状态变化来检测；<br data-start="3727" data-end="3730">
b) <strong data-start="3735" data-end="3744">剪贴板哨兵</strong>值变化。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3751" data-end="3796">
<p data-start="3753" data-end="3796">其中任意一路命中，就认为复制成功再读剪贴板；避免了“没点到复制却写入旧剪贴板”的情况。</p>
</li>
</ul>

scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" tabindex="-1" dir="auto" data-turn-id="d84a7dee-9880-4758-ba00-3d119761e472" data-testid="conversation-turn-44" data-scroll-anchor="true" data-turn="assistant" style="min-height: calc(-248px + 100dvh);"><h6 class="sr-only">ChatGPT 说：</h6><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto pb-10 [--thread-content-margin:--spacing(4)] @[37rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(6)] @[72rem]:[--thread-content-margin:--spacing(16)] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:32rem] @[34rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @[64rem]:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn" tabindex="-1"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div class="absolute flex h-8 w-3 origin-center items-center justify-center" style="opacity: 0; transform: scale(0);"><div class="bg-token-text-primary h-3 w-3 rounded-full"></div></div><div class="relative my-1 min-h-6"><div class="relative flex max-w-[calc(0.8*var(--thread-content-max-width,40rem))] origin-top-left flex-col gap-2 overflow-x-clip" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="" data-state="closed"><div class="relative w-full text-start"><div class="flex w-full items-start justify-between text-start flex-col"><button class="flex w-full items-center gap-0.5"><span class=""><span class="flex items-center gap-1 text-start align-middle truncate text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary" style="opacity: 1;">已思考 35s</span></span></button></div></div></span></div></div><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="cbb944a5-64ce-49a5-bccc-20b096a6e216" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-thinking"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="53">你这次还是回退到纯文本，说明<strong data-start="14" data-end="47">复制动作已点击但没成功把 Markdown 放到系统剪贴板</strong>。常见原因：</p>
<ul data-start="55" data-end="216">
<li data-start="55" data-end="153">
<p data-start="57" data-end="153">页面把内容写进了<strong data-start="65" data-end="75">浏览器剪贴板</strong>（<code data-start="76" data-end="107">navigator.clipboard.writeText</code>），但 Python 的 <code data-start="120" data-end="131">pyperclip</code> 读的是<strong data-start="135" data-end="144">系统剪贴板</strong> → 读不到更新。</p>
</li>
<li data-start="154" data-end="216">
<p data-start="156" data-end="216">“复制”按钮图标已变成对钩（✔），但 <code data-start="175" data-end="187">aria-label</code> 没改成“已复制/Copied”，我们没抓到“成功信号”。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="218" data-end="320">最稳的做法：<strong data-start="224" data-end="239">直接在浏览器里读剪贴板</strong>，而不是用系统剪贴板。Selenium 支持 <code data-start="262" data-end="284">execute_async_script</code> 调 <code data-start="287" data-end="319">navigator.clipboard.readText()</code>。</p>
<p data-start="322" data-end="359">下面给你最小补丁：把这 3 个函数替换到脚本里（其他不动）。它们的顺序是：</p>
<ol data-start="360" data-end="553">
<li data-start="360" data-end="417">
<p data-start="363" data-end="417"><code data-start="363" data-end="395">click_copy_button_in_last_turn</code>：点击最新一条助手消息里的“复制”按钮；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="418" data-end="468">
<p data-start="421" data-end="468"><code data-start="421" data-end="449">read_clipboard_via_browser</code>：用浏览器原生 API 读剪贴板；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="469" data-end="553">
<p data-start="472" data-end="553"><code data-start="472" data-end="496">wait_for_latest_answer</code>：生成完成后，<strong data-start="503" data-end="524">点击复制 → 优先用浏览器读剪贴板</strong>；失败再降级 <code data-start="531" data-end="542">pyperclip</code>；都失败才回退纯文本。</p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="555" data-end="558">
<h3 data-start="560" data-end="583">1) 点击最后一条消息里的“复制”按钮</h3>

class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">get_last_assistant_turn</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv</span></span><span>):
    turns = drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.ASSISTANT_TURN)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">not</span></span><span> turns:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">raise</span></span><span> TimeoutException(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"未找到助手消息 turn。"</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> turns[-</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>]

</span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">click_copy_button_in_last_turn</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv</span></span><span>) -&gt; </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">bool</span></span><span>:
    </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"""滚动到最后一条助手消息，点击其中的【复制】按钮。返回是否点击到。"""</span></span><span>
    turn = get_last_assistant_turn(drv)
    drv.execute_script(</span><span><span class="hljs-string">"arguments[0].scrollIntoView({block:'center'});"</span></span><span>, turn)
    time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.15</span></span><span>)
    btns = turn.find_elements(*SELECTORS.COPY_BUTTON_IN_TURN)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">not</span></span><span> btns:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 兜底：有些皮肤把按钮放到 turn 外层工具条；取最后一个“复制”按钮</span></span><span>
        btns = drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.COPY_BUTTON_IN_TURN)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">not</span></span><span> btns:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">False</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        btns[-</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>].click()   </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 取最后一个最靠近底部的</span></span><span>
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">True</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> Exception:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">False</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>

1.83496H13.5C14.1891 1.83496 14.746 1.83431 15.1963 1.87109C15.6541 1.90851 16.0599 1.98788 16.4365 2.17969L16.6553 2.30176C17.151 2.60585 17.5548 3.04244 17.8203 3.56348L17.8867 3.70606C18.031 4.04235 18.0962 4.40306 18.1289 4.80371C18.1657 5.25395 18.165 5.81091 18.165 6.5V9.33301Z"></path></svg>复制代码</button></div></div></div><div class="overflow-y-auto p-4" dir="ltr"><code class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">read_clipboard_via_browser</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, timeout=<span class="hljs-number">5.0</span></span></span><span>) -&gt; </span><span><span class="hljs-built_in">str</span></span><span>:
    <span class="hljs-string">"""
    直接在页面上下文读 clipboard：navigator.clipboard.readText()
    需要 https 和用户点击手势（我们已点击了复制按钮）。
    """</span>
    end = time.time() + timeout
    last_text = </span><span><span class="hljs-literal">None</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span></span><span> time.time() &lt; end:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 异步脚本：读取剪贴板文本</span></span><span>
            js = <span class="hljs-string">"""
                const done = arguments[0];
                if (!navigator.clipboard || !navigator.clipboard.readText) { done(null); return; }
                navigator.clipboard.readText().then(t =&gt; done(t)).catch(_ =&gt; done(null));
            """</span>
            text = drv.execute_async_script(js)
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> text </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">and</span></span><span> text.strip():
                </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> text != last_text:
                    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> text.strip()
            last_text = text
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> Exception:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span></span><span>
        time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.2</span></span><span>)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-start="2218" data-end="2270">3) 获取回答：点击复制 → 优先用浏览器读剪贴板 → 再用 pyperclip → 最后纯文本</h3>

class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">def</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-title function_">wait_for_latest_answer</span></span><span>(</span><span><span class="hljs-params">drv, timeout</span></span><span>):
    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 等至少一条助手消息</span></span><span>
    wait_for(drv, SELECTORS.ASSISTANT_TURN, timeout)
    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 等生成完（stop→send）</span></span><span>
    wait_until_idle(drv)
    time.sleep(</span><span><span class="hljs-number">0.4</span></span><span>)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># 先点复制按钮</span></span><span>
    clicked = click_copy_button_in_last_turn(drv)

    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># A. 优先：浏览器剪贴板</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> clicked:
        md = read_clipboard_via_browser(drv, timeout=</span><span><span class="hljs-number">6.0</span></span><span>)
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> md:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> md

    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># B. 次选：系统剪贴板（pyperclip）</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">try</span></span><span>:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span></span><span> pyperclip
        md2 = (pyperclip.paste() </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">or</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>).strip()
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> md2:
            </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> md2
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">except</span></span><span> Exception:
        </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span></span><span>

    </span><span><span class="hljs-comment"># C. 兜底：纯文本</span></span><span>
    nodes = drv.find_elements(*SELECTORS.ASSISTANT_MESSAGE)
    fallback = nodes[-</span><span><span class="hljs-number">1</span></span><span>].text.strip() </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span></span><span> nodes </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">""</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span></span><span> </span><span><span class="hljs-string">f"&gt; ⚠️ 未能复制为 Markdown，以下为纯文本回退：\n\n<span class="hljs-subst">{fallback}</span></span></span><span>"
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="3035" data-end="3038">
<h3 data-start="3040" data-end="3055">选择器检查（务必确认）</h3>
<p data-start="3056" data-end="3104">你截图里按钮明确是 <code data-start="3066" data-end="3083">aria-label="复制"</code>。请确保在 <code data-start="3089" data-end="3100">SELECTORS</code> 里有：</p>

class="whitespace-pre! language-python"><span><span>ASSISTANT_TURN = (By.CSS_SELECTOR, </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"[data-message-author-role='assistant'], article[data-message-author-role='assistant']"</span></span><span>)
COPY_BUTTON_IN_TURN = (By.CSS_SELECTOR,
    </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"button[data-testid='copy-turn-action-button'], "</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"button[aria-label*='复制'], button[aria-label*='拷贝'], "</span></span><span>
    </span><span><span class="hljs-string">"button[aria-label*='Copy']"</span></span><span>)
</span></span></code></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="3432" data-end="3531">如果你的界面还会出现“复制为 Markdown”，你也可以在点击失败时再加一段菜单点击逻辑，但上面这版一般足够：<strong data-start="3488" data-end="3502">直接点右上角“复制”</strong>，随后从<strong data-start="3506" data-end="3516">浏览器剪贴板</strong>把 Markdown 读出来。</p>
<hr data-start="3533" data-end="3536">
<h3 data-start="3538" data-end="3549">为什么这版更稳</h3>
<ul data-start="3550" data-end="3680">
<li data-start="3550" data-end="3573">
<p data-start="3552" data-end="3573">不再依赖系统剪贴板与第三方库是否可用；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3574" data-end="3635">
<p data-start="3576" data-end="3635">点击复制后，直接在<strong data-start="3585" data-end="3595">浏览器上下文</strong>读取 <code data-start="3598" data-end="3619">navigator.clipboard</code>，与页面的复制实现是一致的；</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3636" data-end="3680">
<p data-start="3638" data-end="3680">若浏览器权限或策略阻拦，再降级到 <code data-start="3655" data-end="3666">pyperclip</code>；实在不行才落到纯文本回退。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="3682" data-end="3685">
<p data-start="3687" data-end="3844" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">试完这版，如果还回退，请把<strong data-start="3700" data-end="3718">复制按钮节点的完整 HTML</strong>（<code data-start="3719" data-end="3733">&lt;button ...&gt;</code> 那一行）贴我，我再把选择器对得更精确；或者给我看“对钩状态”时按钮的 HTML（看 <code data-start="3776" data-end="3788">aria-label</code> / <code data-start="3791" data-end="3803">data-state</code> 是否变化），我可以在第 1 步里加一个“等待对钩出现”的判断，进一步提升成功率。</p></div></div></div></div><div class="flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 1. Prevent padding and border from affecting element width. (https://github.com/mozdevs/cssremedy/issues/4)
2. Allow adding a border to an element by just adding a border-width. (https://github.com/tailwindcss/tailwindcss/pull/116)

*,

  box-sizing: border-box; /* 1 */
  border-width: 0; /* 2 */

}

/*
1. Use a consistent sensible line-height in all browsers.
2. Prevent adjustments of font size after orientation changes in iOS.
3. Use a more readable tab size.
4. Use the user's configured `sans` font-family by default.
5. Use the user's configured `sans` font-feature-settings by default.
6. Use the user's configured `sans` font-variation-settings by default.
7. Disable tap highlights on iOS
*/

html,
:host {
  line-height: 1.5; /* 1 */
  -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; /* 2 */
  -moz-tab-size: 4; /* 3 */
  -o-tab-size: 4;
     tab-size: 4; /* 3 */
  font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; /* 4 */
  font-feature-settings: normal; /* 5 */
  font-variation-settings: normal; /* 6 */
  -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; /* 7 */
}

/*
1. Remove the margin in all browsers.
2. Inherit line-height from `html` so users can set them as a class directly on the `html` element.
*/

body {
  margin: 0; /* 1 */
  line-height: inherit; /* 2 */
}

/*
1. Add the correct height in Firefox.
2. Correct the inheritance of border color in Firefox. (https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=190655)
3. Ensure horizontal rules are visible by default.
*/

hr {
  height: 0; /* 1 */
  color: inherit; /* 2 */
  border-top-width: 1px; /* 3 */
}

/*
Add the correct text decoration in Chrome, Edge, and Safari.
*/

abbr:where([title]) {
  -webkit-text-decoration: underline dotted;
          text-decoration: underline dotted;
}

/*
Remove the default font size and weight for headings.
*/

h1,
h2,
h3,
h4,
h5,
h6 {
  font-size: inherit;
  font-weight: inherit;
}

/*
Reset links to optimize for opt-in styling instead of opt-out.
*/

a {
  color: inherit;
  text-decoration: inherit;
}

/*
Add the correct font weight in Edge and Safari.
*/

b,
strong {
  font-weight: bolder;
}

/*
1. Use the user's configured `mono` font-family by default.
2. Use the user's configured `mono` font-feature-settings by default.
3. Use the user's configured `mono` font-variation-settings by default.
4. Correct the odd `em` font sizing in all browsers.
*/

code,
kbd,
samp,
pre {
  font-family: Source Code Pro, monospace; /* 1 */
  font-feature-settings: normal; /* 2 */
  font-variation-settings: normal; /* 3 */
  font-size: 1em; /* 4 */
}

/*
Add the correct font size in all browsers.
*/

small {
  font-size: 80%;
}

/*
Prevent `sub` and `sup` elements from affecting the line height in all browsers.
*/

sub,
sup {
  font-size: 75%;
  line-height: 0;
  position: relative;
  vertical-align: baseline;
}

sub {
  bottom: -0.25em;
}

sup {
  top: -0.5em;
}

/*
1. Remove text indentation from table contents in Chrome and Safari. (https://bugs.chromium.org/p/chromium/issues/detail?id=999088, https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=201297)
2. Correct table border color inheritance in all Chrome and Safari. (https://bugs.chromium.org/p/chromium/issues/detail?id=935729, https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=195016)
3. Remove gaps between table borders by default.
*/

table {
  text-indent: 0; /* 1 */
  border-color: inherit; /* 2 */
  border-collapse: collapse; /* 3 */
}

/*
1. Change the font styles in all browsers.
2. Remove the margin in Firefox and Safari.
3. Remove default padding in all browsers.
*/

button,
input,
optgroup,
select,
textarea {
  font-family: inherit; /* 1 */
  font-feature-settings: inherit; /* 1 */
  font-variation-settings: inherit; /* 1 */
  font-size: 100%; /* 1 */
  font-weight: inherit; /* 1 */
  line-height: inherit; /* 1 */
  letter-spacing: inherit; /* 1 */
  color: inherit; /* 1 */
  margin: 0; /* 2 */
  padding: 0; /* 3 */
}

/*
Remove the inheritance of text transform in Edge and Firefox.
*/

button,
select {
  text-transform: none;
}

/*
1. Correct the inability to style clickable types in iOS and Safari.
2. Remove default button styles.
*/

button,
input:where([type='button']),
input:where([type='reset']),
input:where([type='submit']) {
  -webkit-appearance: button; /* 1 */
  background-color: transparent; /* 2 */
  background-image: none; /* 2 */
}

/*
Use the modern Firefox focus style for all focusable elements.
*/

:-moz-focusring {
  outline: auto;
}

/*
Remove the additional `:invalid` styles in Firefox. (https://github.com/mozilla/gecko-dev/blob/2f9eacd9d3d995c937b4251a5557d95d494c9be1/layout/style/res/forms.css#L728-L737)
*/

:-moz-ui-invalid {
  box-shadow: none;
}

/*
Add the correct vertical alignment in Chrome and Firefox.
*/

progress {
  vertical-align: baseline;
}

/*
Correct the cursor style of increment and decrement buttons in Safari.
*/

::-webkit-inner-spin-button,
::-webkit-outer-spin-button {
  height: auto;
}

/*
1. Correct the odd appearance in Chrome and Safari.
2. Correct the outline style in Safari.
*/

[type='search'] {
  -webkit-appearance: textfield; /* 1 */
  outline-offset: -2px; /* 2 */
}

/*
Remove the inner padding in Chrome and Safari on macOS.
*/

::-webkit-search-decoration {
  -webkit-appearance: none;
}

/*
1. Correct the inability to style clickable types in iOS and Safari.
2. Change font properties to `inherit` in Safari.
*/

::-webkit-file-upload-button {
  -webkit-appearance: button; /* 1 */
  font: inherit; /* 2 */
}

/*
Add the correct display in Chrome and Safari.
*/

summary {
  display: list-item;
}

/*
Removes the default spacing and border for appropriate elements.
*/

blockquote,
dl,
dd,
h1,
h2,
h3,
h4,
h5,
h6,
hr,
figure,
p,
pre {
  margin: 0;
}

fieldset {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}

legend {
  padding: 0;
}

ol,
ul,
menu {
  list-style: none;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
}

/*
Reset default styling for dialogs.
*/
dialog {
  padding: 0;
}

/*
Prevent resizing textareas horizontally by default.
*/

textarea {
  resize: vertical;
}

/*
1. Reset the default placeholder opacity in Firefox. (https://github.com/tailwindlabs/tailwindcss/issues/3300)
2. Set the default placeholder color to the user's configured gray 400 color.
*/

input::-moz-placeholder, textarea::-moz-placeholder {
  opacity: 1; /* 1 */
  color: #a1a1aa; /* 2 */
}

input::placeholder,
textarea::placeholder {
  opacity: 1; /* 1 */
  color: #a1a1aa; /* 2 */
}

/*
Set the default cursor for buttons.
*/

button,
[role="button"] {
  cursor: pointer;
}

/*
Make sure disabled buttons don't get the pointer cursor.
*/
:disabled {
  cursor: default;
}

/*
1. Make replaced elements `display: block` by default. (https://github.com/mozdevs/cssremedy/issues/14)
2. Add `vertical-align: middle` to align replaced elements more sensibly by default. (https://github.com/jensimmons/cssremedy/issues/14#issuecomment-634934210)
   This can trigger a poorly considered lint error in some tools but is included by design.
*/

img,
svg,
video,
canvas,
audio,
iframe,
embed,
object {
  display: block; /* 1 */
  vertical-align: middle; /* 2 */
}

/*
Constrain images and videos to the parent width and preserve their intrinsic aspect ratio. (https://github.com/mozdevs/cssremedy/issues/14)
*/

img,
video {
  max-width: 100%;
  height: auto;
}

/* Make elements with the HTML hidden attribute stay hidden by default */
[hidden]:where(:not([hidden="until-found"])) {
  display: none;
}
